{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0113","line_start":400,"line_end":400,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","序论：飞星动盘之必要"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"学习紫微斗数，若仅观察星盘十二宫，只能推断命造的基本格局。然而格局好者未必年年皆好，格局差者未必年年皆差。因此，需将星盘“飞动”，详细研究其人每个年限的运势，此乃斗数精华之所在。","text_sha256":"981d135ab70de38bc41517c31d687ae4810e4dd9364673b6b43c6632f7e3a587","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
