{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0115","line_start":405,"line_end":410,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","总纲：大限起例与十二宫排布"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"一、大限基本规则\n   斗数与子平法相同，以十年为一大限。\n   大限由命宫起：\n   - 阳男、阴女：顺行（顺时针方向数宫位）。\n   - 阴男、阳女：逆行（逆时针方向数宫位）。\n   行至某宫，该宫即为该十年大限之命宫。","text_sha256":"996a0ddeeec9a82c9733676224a7834c6229cb8779ba2d098beb8d86a242e485","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0116","line_start":412,"line_end":414,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","总纲：大限起例与十二宫排布"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"二、大限十二宫排布\n   由大限命宫起，逆排兄弟、夫妻、子女、财帛、疾厄、迁移、交友、官禄、田宅、福德、父母共十二宫。此时不必再理会星盘中原来宫位的名称。\n   （注：大限命宫所在，即为该十年之“本宫”基准点。）","text_sha256":"7377a7b522b700f377da5bd8f23b9fcaa7c4e3322fbaed20a018101a23b006e2","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0117","line_start":416,"line_end":424,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","总纲：大限起例与十二宫排布"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"三、举例说明\n   某阳男命造，木三局。当其在二十三至三十二岁之时，大限命宫在戊辰宫（即原命盘的福德宫）。\n   于是由戊辰宫逆排：\n   - 大限命宫：戊辰\n   - 大限兄弟宫：丁卯\n   - 大限夫妻宫：丙寅\n   - ……\n   - 大限父母宫：己巳\n   至此，即可按各宫所躔星曜组合性质，参考前述诸法进行推断，以知其人此十年间各宫吉凶休咎。","text_sha256":"e32fc8532ef3aeca2ea770a4852c743bf378c9c2b46ec138b834fa3473b17b2b","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0118","line_start":427,"line_end":427,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","技法一：流曜安星法"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【技法一：流曜安星法】","text_sha256":"c057e1b689b4c2db1b049c1968d62da5a04f8eb53a6346f4512fd956f24d08e7","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0119","line_start":429,"line_end":429,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","技法一：流曜安星法"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"排定大限十二宫后，需加入各种属于该大限的“流曜”，方能进行动态推断。","text_sha256":"72d7aa79493f2d99a4574954535ce11a188ae8480832b5d95db1e2c1a90cd90a","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0120","line_start":431,"line_end":436,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","技法一：流曜安星法"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"一、按大限命宫之宫干所取流曜（十干流曜）\n   流化禄、流化权、流化科、流化忌。\n   流禄存、流擎羊、流陀罗。\n   流天魁、流天钺。\n   流文昌、流文曲。\n   （以上流曜之安法，依大限命宫天干，参照安星法口诀排布。）","text_sha256":"dd317603b62a0ba3024e2873c85d693a2196fa8264d6fac6d2b67d68c5bb8bee","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0121","line_start":438,"line_end":439,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","技法一：流曜安星法"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"二、按大限命宫之宫支所取流曜\n   流天马（仅此一曜，依地支安放）。","text_sha256":"6d3921f756a3aa1409004c14b37617eac82763183bee98903423edce15693acf","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0122","line_start":441,"line_end":452,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","技法一：流曜安星法"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"三、举例说明\n   如上例阳男命造，二十三至三十二岁大限命宫在戊辰宫。\n   - 宫干为“戊”，故大限流曜为：\n     流化禄：贪狼\n     流化权：太阴\n     流化科：太阳\n     流化忌：天机\n     流禄存：在巳\n     流擎羊：在午\n     流陀罗：在……（依安星法安入各宫）\n   - 宫支为“辰”，故流天马在寅宫。\n   读者可参照安星法将各流曜安入各宫之内，即可进行大限推断。","text_sha256":"68a107ba963884df1ece4a83e9093efc79f19df7c91246e047ce4d1898063b06","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0123","line_start":455,"line_end":455,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","技法二：流曜力量层级与取舍总则"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【技法二：流曜力量层级与取舍总则】","text_sha256":"6e2c8ec0194c140637df75987f552135fd92386af2ac3124daf3510bd5c136a2","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0124","line_start":457,"line_end":457,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","技法二：流曜力量层级与取舍总则"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"当推断大限、流年、流月、流日时，需严格遵循以下原则。此为年限推断之核心秘要，须细心体会。","text_sha256":"37acc0e83768c5e27a03e5476070b42bd7ec64dcced4749cfb23540d331ad4c0","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0125","line_start":459,"line_end":465,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","技法二：流曜力量层级与取舍总则"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"一、基本法则（针对任一时限）\n   (1) 凡有“流曜”存在时，以流曜为主。原命盘中的相同星曜，若未被流曜冲动，则不起作用。\n       例：命盘中禄存在巳，流禄在申，二者不处三方四正。原擎羊在午，流羊在酉；原陀罗在辰，流陀在未。此时，原盘羊陀禄存对推断虽有影响，但作用不大；反而流禄、流羊、流陀之作用较大。\n   (2) 若原盘星曜与流曜在三方四正冲会，则力量加强，彼此皆发挥作用。\n       例：命盘中禄存在巳，流禄在亥，彼此对冲；擎羊在午，流羊在子；陀罗在辰，流陀在戌，亦彼此对冲。此时力量相加，成为甚为强烈之组合。推断时，全部六颗星曜均起作用。\n   (3) 星曜与流曜冲动之力量比较：\n       以同宫为力量最强；在对宫相冲次之；在三合宫会照又次之。","text_sha256":"a8d6fedfe1409d1af92c7cb37965ff45289af64d57187e5a3371577ca53d1c70","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0126","line_start":467,"line_end":469,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","技法二：流曜力量层级与取舍总则"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"二、大限推断之取舍\n   推断大限时，留意原盘星曜与大限流曜的冲会关系。\n   （即：以本大限之流曜为主，原盘相同星曜被冲动时加入考虑。）","text_sha256":"9e6c91981ca0acbf4d615b9c6c32b870d9f4e528b7bddbeb6ffe5064d48b812d","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0127","line_start":471,"line_end":480,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","技法二：流曜力量层级与取舍总则"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"三、流年推断之取舍\n   推断流年时，留意大限流曜与流年流曜的冲会关系。原星盘的相同星曜力量甚微，除非有两颗流曜同时冲动，否则根本可以不加理会。\n   例：推断流年时，\n   - 原盘禄存在卯，大限禄存在申，流年禄存在寅。\n   - 原盘擎羊在辰，大限擎羊在酉，流年擎羊在卯。\n   - 原盘陀罗在寅，大限陀罗在未，流年陀罗在丑。\n   分析：原盘禄存与大限禄存无照会，又无流年禄存照会，故推断流年时可不予理会。擎羊及陀罗亦如此。\n   但是，大运的羊陀禄与流年的羊陀禄各在对宫冲会，力量彼此加强。因此推断流年时，只需看大运及流年的羊陀禄。\n   再例：命盘禄存在巳，大限禄存在子，流年禄存在亥。原盘禄存虽不与大限禄存会照，但却与流年禄存冲会，因此亦可发生力量。\n   特例：若大限禄存在酉宫，与巳宫原禄存相会；同时，这颗原禄存又有流年流禄在三方冲会。此时，这颗原禄存因同时被大限流禄及流年流禄冲动，其力量绝不能忽视。","text_sha256":"578b0694ee9a581eda416eaca03542c47e988d2f79366e70f77c780d3c7dd515","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0128","line_start":482,"line_end":483,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","技法二：流曜力量层级与取舍总则"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"四、流月推断之取舍\n   推断流月时，只重视流月的流曜及流年的流曜。大限流曜仅在被冲动的情况下才有力量；原星盘中相同的星曜，力量非常之微，可以不加理会。","text_sha256":"215a4654b628094bb1607eabae3cc84ce120325ccc154de8334af387b51dd00b","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0129","line_start":485,"line_end":486,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","技法二：流曜力量层级与取舍总则"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"五、流日推断之取舍\n   推断流日时，力量依次递减。一般来说，大限流曜及星盘中的相同星曜可以不加理会。","text_sha256":"1e7701f6c9644498beee4bcb91695598985e03e539b71adf440b101cb3e5ef1c","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0130","line_start":489,"line_end":489,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","按语"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【按语】","text_sha256":"acfcdad76f0d8427a36057f6ea2f1f385a0ace31b96243bab6f5be24fbf0f4f3","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0131","line_start":491,"line_end":491,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DYNAMIC_LIMIT_YEAR_METHOD","heading_path":["紫微斗数年限推断法","按语"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"以上原则，在推断大限、流年、流月、流日时非常重要，不可忽视。否则花多眼乱，满盘流曜吉凶混杂，若无取舍原则，推断时便可能根本无法判定吉凶星曜同会的性质。学者务必反复演练，方可掌握年限飞动之精髓。","text_sha256":"0ef25565379d82ccccfdf18580dc266a330061041bc01d603ca5330ebd03794d","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0132","line_start":493,"line_end":493,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"========== 大限与流年推断实例详解 ==========","text_sha256":"0415c7870d47e2fc6187b9b86ef03454b10032320edcceefa16145319f2fd009","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0133","line_start":495,"line_end":495,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","命盘基本信息"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【命盘基本信息】","text_sha256":"42b17ff1c05836ac08f2579c78085b09040043a8c6f96274a5b71f0d1269b338","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0134","line_start":497,"line_end":509,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","命盘基本信息"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  命主：女士（阴女）\n  命宫：在未，身宫同宫。天干为乙，无主星。\n  兄弟宫：在午，天干为甲。紫微、天魁、天喜、天姚。\n  夫妻宫：在巳，天干为癸。天机、天马、右弼、孤辰。\n  子女宫：在辰。七杀、文曲化科、阴煞。\n  财帛宫：在卯。太阳化权、天梁、天月、天哭。\n  疾厄宫：在寅。武曲、天相。\n  迁移宫：在丑。天同、巨门化禄。\n  交友宫：在子。贪狼、咸池、红鸾。\n  官禄宫：在亥。太阴、地劫、地空。\n  田宅宫：在戌。廉贞、天府、文昌化忌、擎羊、铃星。\n  福德宫：在酉，无主星。火星、左辅、禄存。\n  父母宫：在申。破军、陀罗。","text_sha256":"5f49261d54b54b461f2956a0fa665ea06de1f55e72f0de2545abdf334489d776","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0135","line_start":512,"line_end":512,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","静态盘面分析：夫妻宫吉凶并集"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【静态盘面分析：夫妻宫吉凶并集】","text_sha256":"cb39a1f73a35944e2c7c547dfb850aef4e9280442e9761fa6daab8c6f49f5b46","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0136","line_start":514,"line_end":514,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","静态盘面分析：夫妻宫吉凶并集"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  命盘中，最值得注意的宫位为夫妻宫。其星系结构分析如下：","text_sha256":"45fe82f5bb5a6937338965836e4066d59a3b9ae7a3fdc6f63488c77a06bbfb1b","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0137","line_start":516,"line_end":517,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","静态盘面分析：夫妻宫吉凶并集"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  一、本宫星曜：\n     天机、右弼、天马同度。","text_sha256":"5db1b1227e146c5de8d8fa5c2ad2234c1853ac0d4ec611bf9315639026b03555","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0138","line_start":519,"line_end":524,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","静态盘面分析：夫妻宫吉凶并集"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  二、三方四正会合：\n     - 会丑宫（迁移宫）：天同、巨门化禄。\n     - 会亥宫（官禄宫）：太阴。\n     - 酉宫（福德宫）：无正曜，须借对宫卯宫之星安宫。\n       借入后为：太阳化权、天梁。\n     - 禄存（在酉宫）亦同时照入。","text_sha256":"acef66bf9d941f54d92c21a9177d8919d26abf6bc0e900ee67067b1fd22089a0","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0139","line_start":526,"line_end":532,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","静态盘面分析：夫妻宫吉凶并集"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  三、初步判断：\n     表面看来，化禄、化权与禄存并照，似可许配偶富贵。\n     然而细察之下，隐患甚多：\n     - 天机本具浮荡性质，与天马同度，浮荡更甚。\n     - 夫妻宫不喜见左辅右弼，此两曜却在夫妻宫同会。\n     - 太阳天梁、天同巨门，均非有利夫妻宫的组合。\n     故此，命盘夫妻宫可谓吉凶并集。是吉是凶，大限的影响至为关键。","text_sha256":"8dd3903ce51552cc6dde266d8f0db6acf59b1a52dc92414dd8df0e66de4ba992","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0140","line_start":535,"line_end":535,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","大限与流年逐限追踪"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【大限与流年逐限追踪】","text_sha256":"876f4e91bdf448ab1c81ae3bad969406a775ddf9b20d134599d8d7a01ca6c93b","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0141","line_start":537,"line_end":537,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","大限与流年逐限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"一、丙申大限（十四至二十三岁）","text_sha256":"f2ebdb94de26d5e092bffa6149609a9aa4ed58f9b163427918ff6160f5da70b8","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0142","line_start":539,"line_end":540,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","大限与流年逐限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   大限命宫：在申。\n   大限夫妻宫：在甲午宫。","text_sha256":"35573250e832c178293103b3f5f42e13917517b745dd8edb8cc2e66e53126dc9","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0143","line_start":542,"line_end":545,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","大限与流年逐限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   大限夫妻宫分析：\n   本宫：紫微。\n   对宫（子宫）：贪狼对照。\n   会合桃花诸曜：红鸾、天喜、咸池、天姚均见。","text_sha256":"80848211aa6bf68813d8ca164fbebcb68480c15f67aa971773f97d896a6b52b2","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0144","line_start":547,"line_end":550,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","大限与流年逐限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   凶象触发：\n   - 会照戌宫的生年文昌化忌，此忌星被大限廉贞化忌在同宫冲起。\n   - 文昌为礼乐之星，廉贞主感情，二者同时化忌，主在此大限中找不到理想伴侣。\n   - 戌宫的擎羊、铃星，又被甲午宫的大限流羊冲起。","text_sha256":"f0c9dd005d5f89d0f3d5ac99027c6595588eb10e15ce528879c40542547383cc","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0145","line_start":552,"line_end":552,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","大限与流年逐限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   结论：此大限必有感情波折，难觅良缘。","text_sha256":"a06a86dca097c1858adf665c2d13182130364d19d9065331ac7440547a6184eb","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0146","line_start":554,"line_end":554,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","大限与流年逐限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"二、丁酉大限（二十四至三十三岁）","text_sha256":"8084c3ae213565299d3d15186e1ecbda411d4e3cfae1556197a1970cb8f96d13","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0147","line_start":556,"line_end":557,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","大限与流年逐限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   大限命宫：在酉（丁干）。\n   大限夫妻宫：在乙未宫。","text_sha256":"dd8332ea2ca1b6219118c8641b46ebbcc93e772e9939d9ce5eb456cb0f9223ba","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0148","line_start":559,"line_end":563,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","大限与流年逐限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   大限夫妻宫分析：\n   - 本宫无正曜，借对宫丑宫（天同、巨门）安星。\n   - 丁干巨门化忌，与原局的巨门化禄组成“忌冲禄”的星系结构。\n   - 同时会合己亥宫的大限太阴化禄、生年太阳化权及天梁。\n   - 阴阳禄权会合，故为结婚的运程。","text_sha256":"b6b6cce5809586832358102fe5c886576ff8b5e858f9f7849269fa7e3b0fd0ac","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0149","line_start":565,"line_end":568,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","大限与流年逐限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   潜藏危机：\n   - 夫妻宫有大限流羊与巨门化忌同守，已暗伏危机。\n   - 会入的太阳天梁与天月同度，为神经系统慢性疾病的星系。\n   - 亥宫（身宫/大限福德宫所在三方）有地劫，整体结构并不理想。","text_sha256":"6e23e5344eed9a151847dc46917dc2f86b0b6838fcbe1fe50c05057badfc3b90","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0150","line_start":570,"line_end":570,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","大限与流年逐限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   结论：此段姻缘实不敢恭维，虽有成婚之象，但根基不稳，暗藏严重问题。","text_sha256":"0aecd841d4d658ba7faba59dca6a594b15c53912f8a57e8a8bed84888d9f3e12","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0151","line_start":572,"line_end":572,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","大限与流年逐限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"三、流年追踪（丁酉大限内）","text_sha256":"950dcf241e22038fecfb0488eddb48cff6f6ec914e2fdfe5103c86fa7303ea70","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0152","line_start":574,"line_end":578,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","一九七八年戊午年"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   【一九七八年戊午年】\n   流年命宫及流年夫妻宫，同会流年贪狼化禄，加上桃花诸曜同度，主“非礼成婚”（奉子/仓促成婚）。\n   流年夫妻宫在壬辰宫：\n   - 有流年陀罗同度，与命盘原局的陀罗冲会。\n   结论：此年结婚之象，但组合并不值得恭维，婚前已有不妥之兆。","text_sha256":"81b2c6cef9f51b95b0858c9e86d4e073251b086e74bd8b3f74c7260163b01c1e","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0153","line_start":580,"line_end":580,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","一九七八年戊午年"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   【一九七九年己未年】结婚。","text_sha256":"db5b4f0c25f0243cc605c759042ecc47b12ad66c0055d35f5f6ca77bed7af9ed","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0154","line_start":582,"line_end":587,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","一九七八年戊午年"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   【一九八三年癸亥年】婚姻破裂。\n   流年夫妻宫：借入卯宫的太阳、天梁、天月一组星曜。\n   - 受丑宫的流年擎羊照会。\n   - 引动巳宫的大限流陀。\n   星系结构触发，导致夫妻感情破裂。\n   原因：丈夫吸毒。（吸毒属于神经系统慢性疾病，正应太阳天梁天月星系之象。）","text_sha256":"aaf197a7dcefa5ff38096389c16ce47467e2c44d7ecef6aabb7b2e5a250d3c47","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0155","line_start":590,"line_end":590,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","延伸分析：福德宫与精神状况"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【延伸分析：福德宫与精神状况】","text_sha256":"5f2e1dfd701b74678042bae4be3263cf13ec87342dc469360668efb8d3364034","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0156","line_start":592,"line_end":592,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","延伸分析：福德宫与精神状况"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   丁酉大限的命宫及福德宫，所会之星系高度一致，皆主精神困扰。","text_sha256":"71e7eccd7fd634a7e2829684bbb2e4702c3f8b9589ee55563a1e6a1c55139873","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0157","line_start":594,"line_end":600,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","延伸分析：福德宫与精神状况"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   大限福德宫（己亥宫）星系结构：\n   - 原局：太阴、地空、地劫。\n   - 会照大限擎羊、大限陀罗。\n   - 会照天机、天马、右弼。\n   - 借入未宫安星的天同、巨门。\n   - 会合太阳、天梁。\n   - 上述星系，多为是非口舌、精神浮动之象征。","text_sha256":"a28535a9e0964ae6b98bee181260aedc48a123c460d46966a7e575b099ad2262","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0158","line_start":602,"line_end":602,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","延伸分析：福德宫与精神状况"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   大限命宫所会，恰为同样之星系。命宫与福德宫同参，精神困扰特别厉害已可断定。","text_sha256":"e5af09c91e039afbf8f3dd5a324f16825fd814aabc2ddf59ed23b40c7a23ae57","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0159","line_start":604,"line_end":611,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","延伸分析：福德宫与精神状况"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   【一九八四年甲子年】自杀事件。\n   流年福德宫：在寅宫，武曲、天相。\n   此宫所受之夹制与冲会极为恶劣：\n   - 受卯宫流年太阳化忌及流年擎羊，与丑宫大限巨门化忌及流年陀罗，构成双重相夹。\n   - 形成“刑忌夹印”、“双忌夹”、“羊陀夹”的三重坏局。\n   - 同时，此组合又构成“铃昌陀武”的凶格。\n   结论：是年精神崩溃，曾经自杀。\n   转机：幸得流年禄存同度，会照午宫大限禄存，故得救不死。","text_sha256":"66ff3577d20ae675feb68a835279824a15fdddd8fa4f1723f22db948cee91a49","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0160","line_start":614,"line_end":614,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","按语"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【按语】","text_sha256":"acfcdad76f0d8427a36057f6ea2f1f385a0ace31b96243bab6f5be24fbf0f4f3","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0161","line_start":616,"line_end":622,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MARRIAGE_LIMIT_YEAR_CASE","heading_path":["大限与流年推断实例详解","按语"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   此例完整展示了如何将静态命盘与大限飞动、流年流曜相结合进行推断。\n   关键要点回顾：\n   1. 先察命盘静态格局，找出吉凶并集的关键宫位（如此例之夫妻宫）。\n   2. 逐大限飞星观察，看大限四化及流曜如何引动原局的吉凶组合。\n   3. 流年推断须紧扣大限流曜与流年流曜的冲会关系，层层递进。\n   4. 命宫与福德宫同参，可全面把握命主物质与精神层面的运势。\n   5. 即使吉凶交叠，亦须精确到具体年份，方可作出准确推断。","text_sha256":"104d45b6f5cd695129d7b3fe302f0e5fe0b9bbae5815154ad290e3d5c35f01a8","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0188","line_start":725,"line_end":725,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"========== 男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷 ==========","text_sha256":"17dcf3c4217a932e6e71bc74956a134be26cafcd8640031524db0a5e21fec376","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0189","line_start":727,"line_end":727,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","命盘基本信息"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【命盘基本信息】","text_sha256":"42b17ff1c05836ac08f2579c78085b09040043a8c6f96274a5b71f0d1269b338","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0190","line_start":729,"line_end":741,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","命盘基本信息"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  命主：男士（阳男）\n  命宫：在亥，天干为癸。天机化忌、火星、天月。\n  兄弟宫：在戌，天干为壬。七杀、左辅。\n  夫妻宫：在酉。太阳化科、天梁、咸池、天喜。\n  子女宫：在申。武曲、天相。\n  财帛宫：在未。巨门、天同、天钺、铃星。\n  疾厄宫：在午。贪狼化禄、擎羊、天哭、天虚。\n  迁移宫：在巳，身宫同宫。太阴化权、禄存。\n  交友宫：在辰。廉贞、天府、陀罗、右弼。\n  官禄宫：在卯，无主星。红鸾、天刑。\n  田宅宫：在寅。破军、天马、地空、孤辰、阴煞。\n  福德宫：在丑，无主星。文曲、文昌、天魁。\n  父母宫：在子。紫微。","text_sha256":"fd7a6afd1101f06dd437e034232db7a8b56b23b11570bab9165b4316129c834b","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0191","line_start":744,"line_end":744,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","静态格局分析"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【静态格局分析】","text_sha256":"2dc3140b197e5f8bcb60febc63528fe1687c44a0c07ebcd2796b5b153f7bcc92","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0192","line_start":746,"line_end":748,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","静态格局分析"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  本命盘最令人注意者，为命宫与迁移宫（身宫）之强烈对比：\n  - 命宫：天机化忌与火星同度。\n  - 迁移宫（身宫）：太阴化权与禄存同度。","text_sha256":"fd07866d17f90c8f72224229fc4a93c1ecafcd0fbceba9a730c763e14357aafb","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0193","line_start":750,"line_end":750,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","静态格局分析"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  由此可推断：其人利于赚取远离出生地之钱财，外地发展优于本地。","text_sha256":"364a329a8c3937f519d5e368b384360f0b9149a7a35554a5dcdadb7484f843a3","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0194","line_start":752,"line_end":756,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","静态格局分析"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  然而，迁移宫亦非全然吉利，须细察其整体结构：\n  - 太阴落陷（在巳宫）。\n  - 会酉宫太阳化科，亦落弱地（酉宫为日落西山之地）。\n  - 太阳天梁组合对照天刑（官禄宫）。\n  - 所会丑宫（福德宫）无正曜，须借未宫星曜安宫。借入后为：天同、巨门、铃星、天钺。","text_sha256":"19e5802abaca9c2aff5386390daada05ed74fc55dc82ff40ce9706abed659579","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0195","line_start":758,"line_end":758,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","静态格局分析"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  综合判断：命主在外地虽可发财，但是非口舌，甚至官非，亦会同时而来。此为吉中藏凶之局。","text_sha256":"888b098c1fca61eee3d137a7b2777f2c83cc4925f3f583147c2654dbf9c6fa2f","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0196","line_start":761,"line_end":761,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","大限追踪：甲寅大限（三十二至四十一岁）"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【大限追踪：甲寅大限（三十二至四十一岁）】","text_sha256":"7093bd9f3869fe0724a3e87b45848823d63b84e9a4495903d45fba252a6a5e38","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0197","line_start":763,"line_end":763,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","大限追踪：甲寅大限（三十二至四十一岁）"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  此为一生中最精彩的运程。","text_sha256":"139773576720f0c928fca1f50340d8ae6cf929e43ef9c6549e86df79b73b7101","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0198","line_start":765,"line_end":766,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","大限追踪：甲寅大限（三十二至四十一岁）"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  大限命宫：在寅。\n  大限迁移宫：在申。","text_sha256":"a051295f2d92616135de1f525129218e804e72f4649843cd711724f6167aa8cd","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0199","line_start":768,"line_end":773,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","大限追踪：甲寅大限（三十二至四十一岁）"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  格局分析：\n  - 迁移宫申宫：武曲化科（大限化科）。\n  - 命宫寅宫：天马（原局）与大限流禄同度。\n  - 构成“禄马交驰”格局。\n  - 且大限流禄冲动午宫贪狼生年化禄（原局疾厄宫）。\n  - 命宫会照流禄，迁移宫武曲化科。","text_sha256":"d22c987f591d0f17872ffccbf8d91e97fa4536c6476e60539ca02b848ca671fc","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0200","line_start":775,"line_end":775,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","大限追踪：甲寅大限（三十二至四十一岁）"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  结论：在此大限之中，命主在外地必能发财，收获甚丰。","text_sha256":"7ca61f65cae902d0aafb0d2b9ea46e26beac50ed44cadb9c3ec9410266d1ab78","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0201","line_start":777,"line_end":781,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","大限追踪：甲寅大限（三十二至四十一岁）"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  大限隐患：父母宫与官非征兆\n  大限父母宫在卯宫（原局官禄宫）：\n  - 卯宫无正曜，须借对宫酉宫星曜安宫。\n  - 借入：太阳（原局化科，但大限丁干太阳化忌）、天梁。\n  - 与原局天刑（卯宫）、大限流羊同度。","text_sha256":"a982079bc36c79a5db5d28d37f11acab994c01f3549945aa65ddc6648cd09cff","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0202","line_start":783,"line_end":785,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","大限追踪：甲寅大限（三十二至四十一岁）"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  推断：\n  - 太阳化忌（大限）与天梁、天刑、流羊同会，主此大限内父亲去世。\n  - 且流年逢卯、酉二宫时，须防官非诉讼。","text_sha256":"4d49a23adb2e5767936cecf31dac87acee56b5882be2886acab1845a2a64b8d1","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0203","line_start":788,"line_end":788,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","流年逐度追踪"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【流年逐度追踪】","text_sha256":"da8cc9592f67b4b2d16f523fa5e0741083913b62115c3374b6d46686f47a44a5","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0204","line_start":790,"line_end":790,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","流年逐度追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"一、庚申年（1980年）","text_sha256":"e4d42faee64d43293877cc9e23ce5f1bc31dc94866fa2ce57d5ce2d4016619f9","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0205","line_start":792,"line_end":793,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","流年逐度追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   流年命宫：在申。\n   流年迁移宫：在寅。","text_sha256":"f6d2e0ef389fe877b542ae3684916785b72a102679bf28e5b297b30c292811fd","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0206","line_start":795,"line_end":798,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","流年逐度追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   流年命宫分析：\n   - 本宫：武曲（大限化科、流年化权）、天相、流年禄存同度。\n   - 流年迁移宫寅宫：飞入流年天马。\n   - 原局命宫寅宫已有天马，现加流年天马，与大限流禄、流年流禄，构成两重“禄马交驰”格局。","text_sha256":"e79e5de781612a9dbfdf5bb7d65293c6d091d25d053bafb9065cfbd3a9c7de84","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0207","line_start":800,"line_end":800,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","流年逐度追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   结论：是年收获甚丰，财运极为畅旺。","text_sha256":"2200be4db9539f17e1b483aeac91e3a9d478fe4f476d5811e4638dc8b5714083","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0208","line_start":802,"line_end":802,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","流年逐度追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"二、辛酉年（1981年）","text_sha256":"bda0592690784b59e688efe1815022703b76602a930f9e97c34cf50e7cebaece","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0209","line_start":804,"line_end":804,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","流年逐度追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   流年命宫：在酉。","text_sha256":"e5561b950593b718877b40d2e3384735f656a389b6a9137fc1f5bc76143d624d","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0210","line_start":806,"line_end":811,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","流年逐度追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   流年命宫分析：\n   - 本宫：太阳（大限化忌）、天梁。\n   - 会合丑宫：文曲（流年化科）、文昌（流年化忌）。\n   - 借入未宫安星：天同、巨门（流年化禄）。\n   - 会合巳宫：太阴（生年化权）、禄存。\n   - 凶象：酉宫有大限流羊、流陀并照，加上天刑、劫煞来会。","text_sha256":"4cf8692adb322ae0480447dc636469444492b2d4de0800e79c56b4c358d59abd","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0211","line_start":813,"line_end":815,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","流年逐度追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   矛盾信号并存：\n   - 吉：仍有流年禄存冲起原局禄存。\n   - 凶：大限化忌、双忌夹、羊陀并照、天刑劫煞并集。","text_sha256":"8cbffdad7bf9bdd9e0665fc35fc5cef4c9f5482724e6b1294f1d330522b24494","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0212","line_start":817,"line_end":817,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","流年逐度追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   结论：是年虽仍有财运（禄存冲动），但主有官讼及破财。","text_sha256":"f6460f2240bc369511577d62ef0e6cb891a1c5ea9d735a72a05cdb06e0747e5e","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0213","line_start":819,"line_end":819,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","流年逐度追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"三、乙丑年（1985年）","text_sha256":"117d2b160fe4ab2d112c886add49db681dc67964c780c8bbb26b25683d46e93a","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0214","line_start":821,"line_end":821,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","流年逐度追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   流年命宫：在丑。","text_sha256":"60aeb58c98950216440da43fc00d1c0b5f2b91065e26074e416f8e447b21bbcd","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0215","line_start":823,"line_end":827,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","流年逐度追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   流年命宫分析：\n   - 丑宫无正曜，借对宫（未宫）星曜安宫。\n   - 借入：天同、巨门、铃星、天钺。\n   - 加会：大限陀罗同度。\n   - 又会合：太阴（流年化忌）、太阳（大限化忌）。","text_sha256":"ba72eda5a4567a541a7b2ea72b328debaa6671b96b57e1c588ba068c376ac067","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0216","line_start":829,"line_end":829,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","流年逐度追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   结论：牵涉入是非纠纷之内。日月双化忌夹制或会照，是非困扰严重。","text_sha256":"b58519c571f64c1264fb41afd43f0142e21e2abac1a7cbdc974b88a55ce0b362","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0217","line_start":832,"line_end":832,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","未来流年预警：丁卯年（1987年）"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【未来流年预警：丁卯年（1987年）】","text_sha256":"b74b9b10e625afda275941003c8f1b5dcbd753f8fd67fe3f977c96b1b03e92da","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0218","line_start":834,"line_end":834,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","未来流年预警：丁卯年（1987年）"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   届时流年命宫在卯。","text_sha256":"7c4c781d296722e11981b8ca877f5841d992931c2f1fb356732a8370833774c3","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0219","line_start":836,"line_end":842,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","未来流年预警：丁卯年（1987年）"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   分析：\n   - 卯宫无正曜，借对宫酉宫星曜安宫。\n   - 借入：太阳（大限化忌）、天梁。\n   - 会合：巨门（流年化禄）、天机（原局化忌）。\n   - 带流年陀罗。\n   - 原局火星（命宫）、铃星（财帛宫）并照。\n   - 更见天刑、大耗、天月等凶曜。","text_sha256":"e876c230e0934f8e1dada6614e5da016f7c0bff5b845ddbb07bac1f8be5dad10","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0220","line_start":844,"line_end":845,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","未来流年预警：丁卯年（1987年）"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   郑重提醒：\n   此年星系组合极为恶劣，化忌重迭，火铃并照，刑耗齐集。命主必须小心谨慎，避免与人纷争，且绝不可卷入是非漩涡，否则恐因官非而遭致重大破财。","text_sha256":"2e1a67898e8628eb5631a04b8bb4d7d6cdfdcb9e2fc8ee9dfa180dee473e360b","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0221","line_start":848,"line_end":848,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","按语：本命例推断要点总结"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【按语：本命例推断要点总结】","text_sha256":"9a1a7fcd970f6b73b00afb996c689f6cdb0929189e064089d36f7b25f8060164","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0222","line_start":850,"line_end":854,"authority":"S10","chapter":"OUTSIDE_DEVELOPMENT_LEGAL_CASE","heading_path":["男命实例详解：外地发迹与官非纠纷","按语：本命例推断要点总结"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  一、身宫在外，禄权居迁移，主外地发展。此为判断事业重心之关键。\n  二、禄马交驰，逢化禄冲动更确，主发迹于外。此为财运格局之重要指标。\n  三、天机化忌守命，易生忧患；若迁移宫吉，宜动不宜静。\n  四、官禄宫无正曜借星，见天刑、太阳化忌，须终身留意官非诉讼。\n  五、大限吉中藏凶，流年逐一引爆。辛酉年官讼破财、乙丑年是非纠纷、丁卯年预警，皆为大限父母宫/官禄宫凶象的逐步兑现。","text_sha256":"8e69cd6ebbb880adf2ef3995e0820d8351a5de89d9bfd943705a5cb31510d8f3","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0223","line_start":856,"line_end":856,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"========== 流月推断法与实例详解 ==========","text_sha256":"2d885ed2ab6257a7a8933cc0e310410d82e114fb748144455e2d56ed259efd38","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0224","line_start":858,"line_end":858,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","总论：流月推断之应用原则"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【总论：流月推断之应用原则】","text_sha256":"fd8b675add566779e4e2601cefc290393b64c4a67f4d8470e9fdffcb0a91b430","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0225","line_start":860,"line_end":861,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","总论：流月推断之应用原则"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"   用斗数推算禄命，不宜经常连流月吉凶都加以推断。因其过于细微，无论吉凶，皆易影响日常情绪。\n   然而，在特定情况下，流月推算则有重要辅助价值。例如：推断是年可能有交通意外，则可借流月推算，找出有凶险的月份，以尽量避免出门驾车。因为人不可能全年不出门，故流月推算能助人趋吉避凶。","text_sha256":"2290322b39f4fb1140aa1d32f8be587fcb5839794b8023a3cb6b2a705a29e939","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0226","line_start":863,"line_end":864,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","总论：流月推断之应用原则"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"   核心原则：\n   推断流月，必须由大限查起，然后查流年，再查流月，方有实际应用意义。目的是帮助趋避。若贸然找一个月份单独推断，则因漫无目的、过于空泛，有时反会陷入迷宫不能自拔。","text_sha256":"6776f70dc4e63cda525d7367fe34eff613bf9e898e925b1b737e3eb9cb3035dc","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0227","line_start":867,"line_end":867,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","实例详解：车祸断骨事件追溯"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【实例详解：车祸断骨事件追溯】","text_sha256":"ca876099a49891fd192af435895ff251f0a4a460c69bd15a8732076a30dfc433","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0228","line_start":869,"line_end":870,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","实例详解：车祸断骨事件追溯"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   命主：某女命。\n   事件：一九七五年（乙卯年）农历五月，驾车失事，并因此断骨。","text_sha256":"41f25e38edc81f07165f3b314ad2a2258a0027b1b2be678c4a70b98a85ac403f","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0229","line_start":872,"line_end":872,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","实例详解：车祸断骨事件追溯"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"一、大限层面分析（事发时所在大限）","text_sha256":"282367a7517b75d5e74951d8a6324ed6910d08b84cb011ee4ee632f35579b04a","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0230","line_start":874,"line_end":881,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","实例详解：车祸断骨事件追溯"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   大限命宫：在申，天干为戊。\n   命宫星系：天同、天梁、地空。\n   三方四正会合：\n     - 对宫（寅宫·大限迁移宫）：无主星，借申宫星曜安宫，即成地空、地劫对拱。\n     - 会子宫（大限官禄宫）：天机（生年化科、大限化忌）、火星。\n     - 会辰宫（大限财帛宫）：太阴（生年化禄）、天刑。\n     - 会戌宫（大限福德宫）：太阳（落陷）。\n     - 会午宫（大限夫妻宫）：巨门（生年化忌），且为羊陀夹忌。","text_sha256":"7d089bc25e24c153363904adc70a18708566688518631acbfd164cc001b8f5a1","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0231","line_start":883,"line_end":894,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","实例详解：车祸断骨事件追溯"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   大限各宫概览：\n     - 大限兄弟宫：在未。天相、擎羊。\n     - 大限夫妻宫：在午。巨门生年化忌、禄存。（羊陀夹忌）\n     - 大限子女宫：在巳。廉贞、贪狼、天马、陀罗。\n     - 大限财帛宫：在辰。太阴生年化禄、天刑。\n     - 大限疾厄宫：在卯。天府。\n     - 大限迁移宫：在寅。无主星，地劫。借申宫星安入。\n     - 大限交友宫：在丑。紫微、破军、铃星。\n     - 大限官禄宫：在子。天机生年化科、大限化忌、火星。\n     - 大限田宅宫：在亥。无主星。\n     - 大限福德宫：在戌。太阳。\n     - 大限父母宫：在酉。七杀、武曲。","text_sha256":"54a98f2e8c2d22aabee473045f90489c715df391c47941b7da4b81431d6dff8d","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0232","line_start":896,"line_end":902,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","实例详解：车祸断骨事件追溯"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   大限格局综合判断：\n     - 天同天梁坐命，地空地劫对拱，已带浮荡不定之象。\n     - 会天机化忌（且为大限忌）、火星，主精神困扰与突发性变动。\n     - 迁移宫借星后，成地空地劫同宫，外出运程根基不稳。\n     - 会巨门生年化忌（且为羊陀夹忌），是非口舌之象强。\n     - 会戌宫落陷太阳，整体气势偏弱。\n     此星系结构，已显示该大限之中可能有凶险，故需逐年追查。","text_sha256":"d983461a1985e13c4d3156ab8f2d5d2d874f8b6676ed5c084d96371170cdc03c","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0233","line_start":904,"line_end":904,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","实例详解：车祸断骨事件追溯"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   （附注：命主于一九七一年辛亥年、一九七三年癸丑年，皆曾撞车，但未受伤。读者不妨自行推断其原因。）","text_sha256":"6fdf27528d99f40f99e9e6ffd283789b4fee8914d631aa8f552af626ff595122","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0234","line_start":906,"line_end":906,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","实例详解：车祸断骨事件追溯"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"二、流年层面分析（乙卯年·1975年）","text_sha256":"722cbbe1f3ed4022b4480c3349303ec5054ed0fea0350b675c03153359006d87","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0235","line_start":908,"line_end":914,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","实例详解：车祸断骨事件追溯"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   流年命宫：在卯。\n   流年命宫分析：\n     - 卯宫为天府坐守。\n     - 恰为流年擎羊及流年陀罗所夹。虽非“夹忌”（天府无化忌之理），但亦属不吉。\n     - 会亥宫（无主星），借巳宫廉贞、贪狼安星，此二曜又恰为大限的流羊、流陀所夹。\n     - 对宫为酉宫：武曲、七杀。\n     - 会未宫：天相，受刑忌夹（巨门化忌与天刑夹天相）。","text_sha256":"8ae1c52fab60dc8fcdd1e58a913ad45071bfe47e51162f6feea7d3009f5c4ca7","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0236","line_start":916,"line_end":921,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","实例详解：车祸断骨事件追溯"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   流年疾厄宫：在戌宫（最关键宫位）。\n     - 本宫：太阳落陷守度。\n     - 会辰宫：太阴（流年化忌，原局化禄）、大限陀罗、流年擎羊、天刑。\n     - 会寅宫：天同、天梁、流年陀罗。\n     - 会午宫：巨门生年化忌（此化忌被大限天机化忌冲起）、大限流羊。\n     煞忌会集极重，故是年主有疾厄。","text_sha256":"6d123324c5f94e461cf90509bb37f44d1586f80fb8e5b1f40e8213ae56c05606","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0237","line_start":923,"line_end":923,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","实例详解：车祸断骨事件追溯"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"三、流月层面分析（锁定乙卯年农历五月）","text_sha256":"a620b68bc82b899e5d0cbb37245823efd0131c607f902720a79850d38de26c38","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0238","line_start":925,"line_end":928,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","实例详解：车祸断骨事件追溯"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   推算步骤：\n     (1) 定斗君：乙卯年斗君在亥宫。\n     (2) 起流月：农历正月由亥宫起行。\n     (3) 至农历五月，流月命宫行至卯宫。此恰与流年命宫重叠，凶象迭加。","text_sha256":"8077576eaf958319ee950ff006063806cd7dbc00412323e5f3d801a019788e5e","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0239","line_start":930,"line_end":935,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","实例详解：车祸断骨事件追溯"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   流月命宫在卯，计算遁干：\n     - 乙卯年正月遁干起戊寅，顺数至五月，命宫干支为壬午。\n     - 壬干使迁移宫（酉宫）武曲化忌。\n     - 命宫卯宫，再为流年羊陀相夹。\n     - 且流月之羊陀将年羊年陀、运羊运陀全数冲起，一齐射入流月疾厄宫（戌宫）。\n     - 戌宫又有月陀与天刑相对，且正曜为太阴化忌拱照。","text_sha256":"2b7943db6235e1d8953db307799ab3fa819c30e32be3e1731d368d616373ef43","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0240","line_start":937,"line_end":941,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","实例详解：车祸断骨事件追溯"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   最终判断：\n     - 流月命宫与流年命宫重叠，已属强信号。\n     - 迁移宫武曲化忌，与七杀同度。武曲属金，七杀肃杀，此组合所显示的性质为“受金属创伤”。\n     - 疾厄宫煞忌并集，太阳落陷，太阴化忌冲照。\n     由此推断，农历五月是一个出行凶险的月份，最需防金属创伤。","text_sha256":"6cd48b613c17a23c151ff85bcba9d4c074c0121e0e113c181461ccf588ee7cff","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0241","line_start":943,"line_end":943,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","实例详解：车祸断骨事件追溯"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   事实印证：命主果于该月驾车失事，导致断骨。","text_sha256":"70a53304dcc183682903abcc1d66e37ee674b5a6045984f2e9dcd602d224aa7b","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0242","line_start":946,"line_end":946,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","按语：流月推断操作要领"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【按语：流月推断操作要领】","text_sha256":"cadad7929d45a64c432c4675de17e0f5a4e3f9b8303228f92d1598ce65e62fee","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0243","line_start":948,"line_end":952,"authority":"S10","chapter":"MONTH_TRAFFIC_CASE","heading_path":["流月推断法与实例详解","按语：流月推断操作要领"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"   一、不为琐事看流月，仅用于避大凶。此为正用。\n   二、推断流月，必须由大限→流年→流月，层层递进，不可跳跃。\n   三、流月命宫与流年命宫重叠，为重要信号，吉凶加倍。\n   四、流月之羊陀可冲起年、运之羊陀，煞曜迭加，往往为应事之月。\n   五、锁定具体宫位：迁移宫看外出安危，疾厄宫看身体损伤。配合正曜化忌性质，可断事之类别（如此例武曲化忌主金属创伤）。","text_sha256":"6c729ce302a79071f3554636010f2a267f027652b51e9bd179795fb9512a4505","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0244","line_start":954,"line_end":954,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"========== 女童患病实例详解 ==========","text_sha256":"f980e01603e0ae54358f6649ef026b626417d9f31a0dd5bf24d1b95e226912fc","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0245","line_start":956,"line_end":956,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","命盘基本信息"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【命盘基本信息】","text_sha256":"42b17ff1c05836ac08f2579c78085b09040043a8c6f96274a5b71f0d1269b338","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0246","line_start":958,"line_end":971,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","命盘基本信息"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  命主：女童\n  生年：壬戌年（1982年）\n  命宫：在酉，天干为己。武曲化忌、七杀。\n  兄弟宫：在申，天干为戊。天梁化禄、天同、天马、左辅。\n  夫妻宫：在未。天相、天月、寡宿。\n  子女宫：在午。巨门、阴煞。\n  财帛宫：在巳。廉贞、贪狼、天钺。\n  疾厄宫：在辰。太阴。\n  迁移宫：在卯。天府化科、天魁。\n  交友宫：在寅，无主星。地空。\n  官禄宫：在丑。紫微化权、破军、文昌、文曲。\n  田宅宫：在子。天机、铃星、擎羊。\n  福德宫：在亥，无主星。禄存。\n  父母宫：在戌。太阳、火星、陀罗。","text_sha256":"3d95246c3a2056e749d5687bed2910871e0dd94c1633f31474df5086ce667b5b","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0247","line_start":974,"line_end":974,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","事件背景"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【事件背景】","text_sha256":"4321eb937d20085dabd6d57576b791c13470159ce03a4ab8e30754bef00f049c","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0248","line_start":976,"line_end":976,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","事件背景"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  女童出生第二年患病，持续不退烧。为其推算后，认为可能是呼吸器官有瘤肿，建议请专科医生详细检查。其父母依嘱送女童入院，经证实为气管有瘤，幸尚未恶化，有治愈之希望。","text_sha256":"8bf73b5252cb5300dbd6c4d5a9ca7a15b5426df509aed7863aa171776e3a3487","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0249","line_start":979,"line_end":979,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","静态命盘分析"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【静态命盘分析】","text_sha256":"36001271210315ebe515b305c56ea14f721f81a4e883dbacc3e15a3af7c7e206","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0250","line_start":981,"line_end":986,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","静态命盘分析"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"  疾厄宫在辰宫，太阴坐守。\n  - 火铃羊陀四煞并照，生而带疾自无疑问。\n  但问题在于：患何种疾病？\n  - 太阴本主阴分亏损之疾。\n  - 然而，命盘的疾厄宫有时并不显示童年所患的病，反而可见于命宫。\n    （此为幼童推断之要诀。）","text_sha256":"5ece78117ccd3cec7ae3a1bcfc3afa26ef7f0463162c9c6cf3237e2f9c8babd4","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0251","line_start":989,"line_end":989,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","逐年童限追踪"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【逐年童限追踪】","text_sha256":"15d2f030fa2f30d918d41902f3eb0d6e564fed678c04ec220148143671f43795","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0252","line_start":991,"line_end":991,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","逐年童限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"一、一岁童限（壬戌年·1982年）","text_sha256":"48b84eb0ce815882e52072f8bb6bc30d1e2941bc75a0dc52961dd8a1d3f27771","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0253","line_start":993,"line_end":996,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","逐年童限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   一岁尚未上运，童限在命宫（酉宫）。\n   流年亦为壬戌年，与生年相同。\n   命宫：武曲化忌、七杀。\n   武曲于壬年化忌，在命宫小限显现。","text_sha256":"163b2d043ba00663b2fdfac4f59d0990b05af1cc4cb9468b518519aaa37cc54b","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0254","line_start":998,"line_end":1001,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","逐年童限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   推断：\n   - 武曲属金，主呼吸系统。\n   - 武曲化忌与七杀同度，主器质性病变。\n   故推断为呼吸器官有瘤肿。","text_sha256":"7851e6a21eff8440192b14442775372b986beb0aaecd5a210dace27efa9ad2bf","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0255","line_start":1003,"line_end":1003,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","逐年童限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"二、两岁童限（癸亥年·1983年）","text_sha256":"0dce7ccf4327ade82b8d775c06df382cf5d0bc8dd5db76c309ea1c3ce772be1b","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0256","line_start":1005,"line_end":1011,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","逐年童限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   童限在财帛宫（巳宫）。\n   流年为癸亥年。\n   财帛宫：廉贞、贪狼、天钺。\n   流年凶象：\n   - 流年羊陀在三方会照小限。\n   - 宫内贪狼于癸年化为忌星。\n   - 更会天刑、劫煞、大耗诸杂曜。","text_sha256":"0ce6a58b5440c57e26e7ae250ca3130d92ae551894dce8ceb1a3b0cff1c2a3c2","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0257","line_start":1013,"line_end":1016,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","逐年童限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   推断：\n   - 贪狼化忌与消耗性杂曜同会，主所患之病带损耗性质。\n   事实印证：\n   - 此年女童接受放射治疗，体质自然亏损。","text_sha256":"4a109c44e75319205179db13f2c45e2cac170d1be96c86e8a1ec3b823f675b0e","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0258","line_start":1018,"line_end":1018,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","逐年童限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"三、三岁童限（甲子年·1984年）","text_sha256":"c7db74bde74125f6a30f13bcb0f5309a86f4edda7166b263d25df10f185657f0","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0259","line_start":1020,"line_end":1026,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","逐年童限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   童限在疾厄宫（辰宫）。\n   流年为甲子年。\n   疾厄宫：太阴坐守。\n   流年凶象：\n   - 太阴拱照太阳化忌（太阳在戌宫，甲干太阳化忌）。\n   - 兼且火铃羊陀四煞并照。\n   - 病情反复之极。","text_sha256":"d4ff996f6076bdd36924dafb7e974d049ba91019b9e0a275e4be7715ffb449f8","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0260","line_start":1028,"line_end":1031,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","逐年童限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   转机：\n   - 后幸能渡过，依赖天梁（在申宫）及华盖照会之力。\n   - 且天盘原有羊陀，未被流年羊陀冲起，故力量未深。\n   - 天盘原有禄存（亥宫）、天府化科（卯宫）亦起到扶持作用。","text_sha256":"f91d5c2ca5a09565133ec2de8ebf9911710d2e1ddf9f9e01619ae0274c8eaed9","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0261","line_start":1033,"line_end":1033,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","逐年童限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   结论：此年为大灾之年，病情反复，幸得吉星照会且煞曜未被全数冲动，方得渡过。","text_sha256":"f6da9b6a15d28ee88c5cd80798fbd02ca7606dbcbdeab38bb058da33c780aa79","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0262","line_start":1035,"line_end":1035,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","逐年童限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"四、四岁童限","text_sha256":"502a2103a888e36bdd52df58e6761c901488ed9a0f367d849b4b1222379bbc96","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0263","line_start":1037,"line_end":1038,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","逐年童限追踪"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   渐告有起色。\n   - 得天寿拱照，未尝无灾，但整体向好。","text_sha256":"7b2d617b04a6ad3675789aeb9241238503b15b6b32961e3d94b1e5bf946388f9","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0264","line_start":1041,"line_end":1041,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","特殊说明：关于夭折的推断"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【特殊说明：关于夭折的推断】","text_sha256":"676bfa61e5936b75b52ffe44ce3a7a5349e69e72a49590a89b91082086060736","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0265","line_start":1043,"line_end":1045,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","特殊说明：关于夭折的推断"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   这种命造，很难确定是否夭折，因为与祖德有关。\n   - 女童的父母皆温厚纯良，所以三岁的大灾能安然渡过，可谓侥天之幸。\n   - 祖德（祖先与父母之德泽）对幼童命盘有重大影响，此为推断之变数，不可机械论断。","text_sha256":"d65108b96299e68e6cb4d1bb531f8735b3b566ce9d10c3d7e732e04985d1dbe4","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0266","line_start":1048,"line_end":1048,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","按语：幼童推断要点总结"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【按语：幼童推断要点总结】","text_sha256":"87db94bc2f4c2a5151bcc1d33225887f9badf24755e243021bf75cebb4f52278","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0267","line_start":1050,"line_end":1055,"authority":"S10","chapter":"CHILD_ILLNESS_CASE","heading_path":["女童患病实例详解","按语：幼童推断要点总结"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"   一、童年疾病，疾厄宫未必应事。一岁童限看命宫，此为首要经验。\n   二、武曲化忌与七杀同度，在命宫或疾厄宫，主呼吸系统器质性病变（如瘤肿）。\n   三、贪狼化忌会天刑、劫煞、大耗，主损耗性疾病或需经历损耗性治疗（如放疗）。\n   四、四煞并照于疾厄宫或命宫，生而带疾，须逐年追查童限以定性。\n   五、幼童命盘不可孤立推断，须参考父母品行及祖德。此为中州派重视之“天地人”三盘之外因。\n   六、病情能否渡过，流年羊陀是否冲动原盘羊陀，以及有无天梁、华盖等救应星曜，均为关键判断依据。","text_sha256":"26118496952773c3c8cc8903881e5d0505ee48717cfd9aae43b834dcc57b5b66","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0268","line_start":1057,"line_end":1057,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"========== 流日流时推断法 ==========","text_sha256":"c142706ac062a2bc912b9e71026fa06b79fe3e8e03f7a671f6cefaf622950d29","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0269","line_start":1059,"line_end":1059,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","总论：流日推断之应用原则"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【总论：流日推断之应用原则】","text_sha256":"d9dbca27bffe3529ee840cf84c3ce7c231548df302452bdaeab87fe179a96caf","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0270","line_start":1061,"line_end":1061,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","总论：流日推断之应用原则"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"   笔者并不主张研究斗数者经常推断流日。因为“水太清则无鱼，人至察则无徒”，不宜将运程推断得太过仔细。过细则易生执念，反为所累。","text_sha256":"fce21dfed3cf0a732104c65793345dd1cff8a790fc9daec1ec5465278e553298","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0271","line_start":1063,"line_end":1065,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","总论：流日推断之应用原则"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"   但在个别特殊情形之下，推断流日又有其必要：\n   一、为弥留状态之病人推断死期，以便家人有所准备。\n   二、在已推断可能发生交通意外的月份中，若不得不择日出门，便可借流日推断挑选相对安全之日。","text_sha256":"40487d86136dbe394e49c5f68eb22e921d6b1a52ef2de68719fe6a4c2b06d573","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0272","line_start":1067,"line_end":1067,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","总论：流日推断之应用原则"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"   此为正用，目的在趋吉避凶与尽人事之安排。","text_sha256":"eaaeb63ebedca8bc6eb3e4a2184e13c4bb9de31877115fd74b5b62d3a797757e","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0273","line_start":1070,"line_end":1070,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","流日命宫定法"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【流日命宫定法】","text_sha256":"b41bc3ee511b66c80a02bc382c147591a7e8aa7b0e10dd40c57fc538bb5829ac","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0274","line_start":1072,"line_end":1075,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","流日命宫定法"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"   流日的推断，以流月命宫为起点。\n   步骤：\n   一、定流月命宫所在之宫位。\n   二、以该宫为初一，顺行（顺时针）数至要推断之日，所落之宫即为当日的“流日命宫”。","text_sha256":"455a00b43048eb22e6a693481534215aaecfd3c199d05f331529e82674bd9c01","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0275","line_start":1077,"line_end":1081,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","流日命宫定法"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"   举例说明：\n   - 四月流月命宫在戌宫。\n   - 即戌宫为初一，顺行：\n       初二在亥宫，初三在子宫，初四在丑宫。\n   - 故四月初四之流日命宫在丑宫。","text_sha256":"6be2c3dab9ee961bb9df169e7729641a994190690b213322c132c6a8cc57c133","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0276","line_start":1084,"line_end":1084,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","流日流曜安法"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【流日流曜安法】","text_sha256":"aef7d029bd6ca6de8bf978c4144e818c97b738ebfa09b2c7c69cc1f16724135f","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0277","line_start":1086,"line_end":1086,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","流日流曜安法"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"   定出流日命宫后，须参照日历（或万年历）查找当日干支，再以此干支安放流日流曜。","text_sha256":"82ec3e21019c352cb87bbfe4f681e427311d19dabd02498286d9babab5aa2cdc","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0278","line_start":1088,"line_end":1092,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","流日流曜安法"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"   接上例：\n   - 乙丑年四月初四日，干支为壬戌。\n   - 则以“壬戌”干支找寻流曜：\n       天梁化禄、紫微化权、天府化科、武曲化忌。\n       禄存在亥……（依安星法安入各宫）。","text_sha256":"57adc4227627817adafef0b1541e6043b4e0c45dd1275aa7549644099f74c6dc","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0279","line_start":1095,"line_end":1095,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","闰月处理规则"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【闰月处理规则】","text_sha256":"483731752d54dad64d42941852cd5d63b4c01f8f02dd3bf8156d2105367ffcc4","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0280","line_start":1097,"line_end":1100,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","闰月处理规则"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"   若遇闰月，处理规则如下：\n   一、上半月（初一至十五）属前一个月，用前月之流月干支。\n   二、下半月（十六至廿九/三十）属后一个月，用后月之流月干支。\n   三、流日仍顺轮不断。","text_sha256":"6b195e56d80ad9d46911b9599bf62f313b4a1b1c4ae27a1ec2f3be692639784f","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0281","line_start":1102,"line_end":1104,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","闰月处理规则"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"   举例说明（甲子年闰十月）：\n   - 闰十月初一至十五日：属十月。\n   - 闰十月十六日至二十九日：属十一月。","text_sha256":"0986a86e562ff885ea0ed0db7d209039b5d654dbfb80b5488f33890e059034c0","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0282","line_start":1106,"line_end":1113,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","闰月处理规则"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"   流日顺轮详解：\n   - 假定十月流月命宫在酉。\n   - 由酉宫起初一，顺数：\n       至十五日仍在酉宫附近顺轮。\n       至二十五日返回酉宫。\n       至三十日行至寅宫。\n   - 接着顺数不停，闰十月初一以卯宫为流日命宫。\n   - 查万年历，是日为辛酉日，故以“辛酉”干支找寻流曜。","text_sha256":"804d3c33322c8775cd3dc219ae3356e7cdf254c9427aef73e4ad31ef1f0b490d","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0283","line_start":1115,"line_end":1117,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","闰月处理规则"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"   - 闰十月十六日起，改以十一月流月命宫（即戌宫）为基准起顺行。\n   - 流月干支用十一月干支（即丙子月）。\n   - 流日干支仍以当日万年历记载为准。","text_sha256":"fd1580c63172f73a476e4dda70ca1a0359dd18b7c7c552fb879771fb0d1e62ac","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0284","line_start":1120,"line_end":1120,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","流时推断法"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【流时推断法】","text_sha256":"dbb7f0bf6ee524f8e010b98f3b9278990b7faca2082768f9a0ed13cac5f52b53","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0285","line_start":1122,"line_end":1122,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","流时推断法"],"role":"EDITORIAL_SUPPLEMENT","contribution_mode":"ZERO_EDITORIAL","text":"   （按：原文此部分未展开详述。推断原理与流日相类，由流日命宫起子时，顺行至所求时辰之宫位，即为流时命宫，再依该时辰干支安放流曜。）","text_sha256":"0be691cd25c5c0075b7807cc670bb4d08e3bbeabd7bd6f1409faaf5472c461c1","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO","status":"REFERENCE_ONLY","editorial_pollution":"YES","runtime_rule_authority":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0286","line_start":1125,"line_end":1125,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","按语"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【按语】","text_sha256":"acfcdad76f0d8427a36057f6ea2f1f385a0ace31b96243bab6f5be24fbf0f4f3","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0287","line_start":1127,"line_end":1130,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","按语"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"   流日流时推断，为紫微斗数最细微之推步。非必要不轻用，用之则须有明确目的。\n   其推算方法为：\n   流月命宫定初一 → 顺数至日 → 得流日命宫 → 查日干支安流曜。\n   闰月则上半月属前月，下半月属后月，流日顺轮不间断。","text_sha256":"2038120cfad1f3d8355efaa62e5b3c6f53cd369b31c868bf93095492aefaf4bb","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0288","line_start":1132,"line_end":1132,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_HOUR_METHOD","heading_path":["流日流时推断法","按语"],"role":"GENERAL_SOURCE_RULE","contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_BASE","text":"   此套方法与前述大限、流年、流月推断法一脉相承，共同构成紫微斗数由宏至微的完整飞星动盘体系。","text_sha256":"11f0860a5a1ab510d3f19167393399e3dc84e0e9d7a19401ff3759b414a0f79c","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0289","line_start":1134,"line_end":1134,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"========== 日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录 ==========","text_sha256":"21b24b0e88bede5d14c5952f539fdeeb60441c0c51826e39b34abf5655f535d7","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0290","line_start":1136,"line_end":1136,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","命盘信息"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【命盘信息】","text_sha256":"c6e65b61a6a7e4c0268b807c60b0dcbeca1eb0797c77a2723e1e954e0c4c7ec7","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0291","line_start":1138,"line_end":1139,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","命盘信息"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"命主：某女士，阳女。\n正行大限：乙未大限。","text_sha256":"0e01018e2c9bd35dab23e696ef190ea321b9a7a2bcbffb4e903177acc7e34ad7","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0292","line_start":1141,"line_end":1153,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","命盘信息"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"大限十二宫分布：\n  大限命宫：未宫。无主星，天月、地劫。\n  大限兄弟宫：午宫。紫微、铃星、擎羊、右弼。\n  大限夫妻宫：巳宫。天机生年化权、禄存、大耗、天姚、天巫。\n  大限子女宫：辰宫。七杀、陀罗、天虚。\n  大限财帛宫：卯宫。太阳、天梁、地空。\n  大限疾厄宫：寅宫。武曲、天相。\n  大限迁移宫：丑宫。巨门、天同生年化禄、天刑、破碎。\n  大限交友宫：子宫。贪狼、文曲、天福、月解、天寿。\n  大限官禄宫：亥宫。太阴、天喜、天魁。\n  大限田宅宫：戌宫。廉贞生年化忌、天府。\n  大限福德宫：酉宫。无主星，火星、天钺。\n  大限父母宫：申宫。破军、天马、左辅、天哭。","text_sha256":"975e37861095df5378079802503eea4dbbe1d07d64ab8dc7f0c8a86e73bd15be","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0293","line_start":1156,"line_end":1156,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","大限层面分析：乙未大限"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【大限层面分析：乙未大限】","text_sha256":"99518c71557d3795b25978c2ad25d23bce345969868cefaeac069497cc5f2528","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0294","line_start":1158,"line_end":1161,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","大限层面分析：乙未大限"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"未宫无正曜，借丑宫星曜入宫安星：\n  借入：巨门、天同、天刑。\n  同时与卯宫的地空、大限命宫的地劫相会。\n  形成天刑、天月同度，地劫地空相会的结构。","text_sha256":"c78a023ce4016a814f0ea37fbb2b5282e2f5f36ed46598cb2919cc38b20ac699","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0295","line_start":1163,"line_end":1165,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","大限层面分析：乙未大限"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"天同巨门本主神经线疾病，尤其与骨殖神经有关。\n天刑、天月为疾病缠绵之兆，会将病况拖延，使患者有如受刑。\n会合太阳天梁，进一步强化此类慢性病征。","text_sha256":"b2deec5bfa78ad7acaa8f94cc9361cb4b60e11af50d6f6eaccb42f76edecf7e1","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0296","line_start":1167,"line_end":1168,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","大限层面分析：乙未大限"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"判定：\n  在此大限之内，命主可能患上此类疾病，且必为慢性，病程反复，难以在短期内彻底痊愈。","text_sha256":"8b4620240e85fc6585a4b9ae51f1b38865e1396a555a717476ad9d837640641c","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0297","line_start":1171,"line_end":1171,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","流年追踪：壬戌年"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【流年追踪：壬戌年】","text_sha256":"0bf40ce5ecd1168c5e985d7049ce6cacc363a8cbe7d2457b0829eb86d5e51c3f","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0298","line_start":1173,"line_end":1181,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","流年追踪：壬戌年"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"流年命宫：戌宫。\n本宫：廉贞生年化忌、天府。\n流年凶象叠加：\n  廉贞化忌会武曲流年化忌。\n  流年陀罗飞入戌宫，\n    冲动辰宫陀罗及大限流羊，\n    又冲动大限流陀。\n  子宫的流年擎羊及寅宫的大限流陀，\n    冲起午宫的擎羊、铃星来会。","text_sha256":"267dc031a34d130fb3a792c35e58f286f4be59e9afcbadd1c904ee7acb8f6843","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0299","line_start":1183,"line_end":1183,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","流年追踪：壬戌年"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"由此可断，是年必有灾厄。","text_sha256":"976770baae5e135c1737792cbb9ea9fa33805f4a94ec7fc36ab269303e139ab5","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0300","line_start":1185,"line_end":1188,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","流年追踪：壬戌年"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"性质推断：\n  武曲化忌冲起廉贞化忌，一般均主血光之灾。\n  此年迁移宫在辰，七杀坐守，并非在外埠受血光灾厄。\n  女命血光可为生育、落胎、脓疮之疾，亦可为金属创伤。","text_sha256":"4421cfc7b9e589e783e59c7a0c352dd2f9dea07437a288690239fe7491511481","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0301","line_start":1190,"line_end":1197,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","流年追踪：壬戌年"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"追查流年疾厄宫（巳宫）：\n  天机守度。\n  被两颗皆冲动的擎羊所夹。\n  与太阴化忌正照。\n  擎羊主伤；\n  太阴与天机相会，主神经系统疾患。\n  又与丑宫的天同巨门及天刑相会，\n  更与酉宫由卯宫借入的太阳天梁会合。","text_sha256":"48af9124b4a885c4bd99ecd9a0777e0b4864a2f4445fb0583a2819d171fade7d","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0302","line_start":1199,"line_end":1200,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","流年追踪：壬戌年"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"综合判定：\n  此年所受之灾为意外伤，影响骨殖神经线，与神经系统疾病相关。","text_sha256":"c99ab4dc9e9fdf092f4f2fcefc357070056ac91744b80832cfa60b7d40ca64e3","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0303","line_start":1203,"line_end":1203,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","流月追踪：壬戌年正月"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【流月追踪：壬戌年正月】","text_sha256":"8a4494d8f1b3f1051675e3a9aa6e9eced49d482f39b293f56d142c7ef93e5579","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0304","line_start":1205,"line_end":1212,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","流月追踪：壬戌年正月"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"定流月：\n  壬戌年正月起壬寅。\n  戌年斗君恰在寅宫，故以寅宫为流月命宫。\n  壬寅月，武曲再化一次忌，与年化忌相叠，力量甚大。\n  再与戌宫的年陀、月陀相会，\n  又与午宫的擎羊、铃星相会。\n  （午宫此两星的三方四正，受大限流陀、年陀、月陀、年羊、月羊冲起，\n   故虽为原盘星曜，对流月命宫依然有作用。）","text_sha256":"30cc696409950279940057ee395fa62081bc9f5e3f2f83c5b058185c13ab10dc","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0305","line_start":1214,"line_end":1215,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","流月追踪：壬戌年正月"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"判定：\n  此月运程颇为不妙，需特别谨慎。","text_sha256":"2118a63403ca8a6c2de8e96197a93f29136f795d45a2daa65458be47758ee678","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0306","line_start":1218,"line_end":1218,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","流日追踪：壬戌年正月初五（壬子日）"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【流日追踪：壬戌年正月初五（壬子日）】","text_sha256":"76f46d27849b8418cdad0e253c757f0b3c5c94826885e4b5b7165ea036127182","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0307","line_start":1220,"line_end":1223,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","流日追踪：壬戌年正月初五（壬子日）"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"流日命宫：午宫。\n  因日干为壬，寅宫武曲再化一次忌，成为“武曲三化忌”。\n  冲动戌宫的廉贞化忌。\n  三方四正共会上八点羊陀及铃星，煞曜极重。","text_sha256":"d964c2ddba2ff996f4920441047ad7fd2f06fa74a9b7967f14f6a4357c74cc8d","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0308","line_start":1225,"line_end":1227,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","流日追踪：壬戌年正月初五（壬子日）"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"是日疾厄宫：丑宫。\n  天同巨门及天刑守度。\n  又为流日化忌与流日擎羊所夹。","text_sha256":"3b5f87a6df0e101bde9ea79408737f55f6dfd05654d3ec056d48c8c9aebff268","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0309","line_start":1229,"line_end":1232,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","流日追踪：壬戌年正月初五（壬子日）"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"事实印证：\n  命主于一九八二年壬戌年农历正月初五发生车祸骨折，流血。\n  医愈之后，仍骨病缠绵。\n  为骨殖神经受伤之故，成终生疾患，至今仍须作物理治疗。","text_sha256":"603172a0d31b2afaa9fb7952e86e94ea97996d536b28f15472a6ca05055f01f3","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0310","line_start":1235,"line_end":1235,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","婚姻影响：乙丑年（1985年）警示"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【婚姻影响：乙丑年（1985年）警示】","text_sha256":"69283b9b49cf58a0e92f45760761d78816e0aee17ac185ecf2be74d051c57131","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0311","line_start":1237,"line_end":1240,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","婚姻影响：乙丑年（1985年）警示"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"车祸后，因性生活受到影响，丈夫因而变心。\n至乙丑年（1985年），出现离婚危险。\n读者不妨由壬戌年（1982年）起，追赶查看每个流年与夫妻宫之变化，\n即可见到婚姻从此竖起红旗。","text_sha256":"363bb2e10330692c5614f775278308bbd2fe9ca2775c1abfee508d3d27581272","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0312","line_start":1243,"line_end":1243,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","趋避与修身提示"],"role":"CONTROL_HEADING","contribution_mode":"ZERO_CONTROL","text":"【趋避与修身提示】","text_sha256":"94ff6b659948d3719995ba81c7d98fa92954b0763d537e4ca01a307c6ca1d9d9","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
{"paragraph_id":"ZZTERM-P-0313","line_start":1245,"line_end":1247,"authority":"S10","chapter":"DAY_ACCIDENT_MARRIAGE_CASE","heading_path":["日盘实例：车祸骨折与婚姻危机的推演全纪录","趋避与修身提示"],"role":"CASE_METHOD_ONLY","contribution_mode":"CASE_RESULT_ZERO","text":"若该女士正月初五静居家中，不驾车外游，\n则正月初九丙辰日、正月廿五壬寅日，仍主有灾。\n（读者可自行飞星推断，追查缘故。）","text_sha256":"a9d3f29fdd3745edb7bb2951b21da7ce989b1e171ca6ed86bac9c086091ed679","direct_event_permission":"NO","direct_endpoint_permission":"NO","direct_score_permission":"NO"}
