{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0118","source_sequence":118,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":403,"source_line_end":409,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷三·天地人三盘四化轨道与突破性发现","parent_section":"二、天地人三盘四化之轨道原理","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"当前几乎所有的命相家都在飞四化，不外乎以大限为媒介，上应本命，\n下应流年。\n  本命盘看定数。\n  活盘看应数。\n  本命盘化给大限用，大限化给流年用，流年复化回去给本命盘用──\n  此称为天人合一。\n  此种天地人盘之理则是正确的。","raw_text_sha256":"419b2bf93f765037d11507403794f90cf2b99042c27c8117503bda9ae7a3c62f","clause_ids":["HL-C-0118-01","HL-C-0118-02","HL-C-0118-03","HL-C-0118-04","HL-C-0118-05","HL-C-0118-06","HL-C-0118-07"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0118-01","HL-R-0118-02","HL-R-0118-03"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","NEGATION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":["本命","大限","流年"],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
