{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0121","source_sequence":121,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":416,"source_line_end":422,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷三·天地人三盘四化轨道与突破性发现","parent_section":"二、天地人三盘四化之轨道原理","parent_subsection":"天干不变之理","raw_text":"正宗的河洛紫微斗数，由命、限、年、月、日、时一路往下推，天干\n一律不变。\n原因：人类呱呱坠地之刹那，在地球表面某一坐标（某一经纬度）上，\n与天体诸星球之割切，产生了一则命造之命质命能──即本命盘。\n由此命质命能，导引出一条抛物线──即行限盘，包含限、年、月、\n日、时盘。\n本命盘看定数，行限盘看应数，无不尽在其中。故天干不变之理自明。","raw_text_sha256":"fa9a00acafdee8a2ef8d026a5a0f543f9cc23777e20d2d98dbb549aeeba04bdf","clause_ids":["HL-C-0121-01","HL-C-0121-02","HL-C-0121-03","HL-C-0121-04","HL-C-0121-05","HL-C-0121-06","HL-C-0121-07","HL-C-0121-08"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0121-01","HL-R-0121-02","HL-R-0121-03","HL-R-0121-04","HL-R-0121-05"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CAUSAL","NEGATION","SEQUENCE"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":["紫微"],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":["本命"],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
