{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0124","source_sequence":124,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":428,"source_line_end":433,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷三·天地人三盘四化轨道与突破性发现","parent_section":"三、活盘不重叠与流日应期秘法","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(一) 活盘永不重叠\n   大限管十年，流年宫位有十二。\n   流年每绕一圈，与大限割切之角度永远不同。\n   流月与年盘割切之角度，亦永远不同。\n   每日与时盘割切之角度，也永远不同。\n   因此，人自出生那一刻起，直至死亡，活盘永远不会重叠。","raw_text_sha256":"0cf548e4c7bb012a08617145d6711b4a6b3991024e9a31069887916ead884701","clause_ids":["HL-C-0124-01","HL-C-0124-02","HL-C-0124-03","HL-C-0124-04","HL-C-0124-05","HL-C-0124-06"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0124-01","HL-R-0124-02","HL-R-0124-03","HL-R-0124-04","HL-R-0124-05","HL-R-0124-06"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":["大限","流年","流月"],"topic_tags":["HEALTH_RISK"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":["死亡"],"risk_tags":["ENDPOINT_CANDIDATE_ONLY","EXTREME_ENDPOINT_LIMIT"],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":true}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0125","source_sequence":125,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":435,"source_line_end":440,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷三·天地人三盘四化轨道与突破性发现","parent_section":"三、活盘不重叠与流日应期秘法","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(二) 日盘之重叠规律\n   唯有日会重叠。\n   每月有二十九或三十日。\n   初一、十三、二十五日，会在同一宫位与月盘之角度重叠。\n   初二、十四、二十六日重叠。\n   （依此类推）","raw_text_sha256":"67ea44ce6714e68232ff3cf6993fd0571352c419c9c8188ae1633fa0260902f0","clause_ids":["HL-C-0125-01","HL-C-0125-02","HL-C-0125-03","HL-C-0125-04","HL-C-0125-05","HL-C-0125-06"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0125-01","HL-R-0125-02","HL-R-0125-03","HL-R-0125-04","HL-R-0125-05"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONTRAST","ALTERNATIVE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
