{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0127","source_sequence":127,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":446,"source_line_end":451,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷三·天地人三盘四化轨道与突破性发现","parent_section":"三、活盘不重叠与流日应期秘法","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(三) 不传之秘：流日应期断法\n   看流日，要先看命造之生日，是生于月旬中之上旬、中旬、还是\n   下旬。\n   例如：事故将发生在某一月，但应于哪一天？\n   以最接近生日的这一圈，为事故发生之时。\n   此为不传之秘，特此公开。","raw_text_sha256":"6237fbd572f142ea133e8a26ba47fff27f3bd596fd4bf20aa7e18d6a4b698b41","clause_ids":["HL-C-0127-01","HL-C-0127-02","HL-C-0127-03","HL-C-0127-04","HL-C-0127-05","HL-C-0127-06"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0127-01","HL-R-0127-02","HL-R-0127-03","HL-R-0127-04","HL-R-0127-05","HL-R-0127-06","HL-R-0127-07"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CAUSAL","NEGATION","CONTRAST","SEQUENCE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":["流日"],"topic_tags":["HEALTH_RISK"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":["事故"],"risk_tags":["ENDPOINT_CANDIDATE_ONLY"],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
