{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0129","source_sequence":129,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":455,"source_line_end":459,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷三·天地人三盘四化轨道与突破性发现","parent_section":"三、活盘不重叠与流日应期秘法","parent_subsection":"按语：要点总结","raw_text":"一、忌星之害，以冲宫之交友宫为最凶。源于一六共宗之理。\n二、同步断诀以天干不变为基，由命盘直贯限、年、月、日、时。\n三、活盘永不重叠，唯日盘有周期性重叠。应期判断须结合命主出生日\n   之旬位。\n此三项，为方外人河洛紫微斗数之独到心法，学者宜深加体会。","raw_text_sha256":"44101d206f82a0d31dcb406a9f914ac7a3be71ff25c4a8f74943eda9f6e7ac00","clause_ids":["HL-C-0129-01","HL-C-0129-02","HL-C-0129-03","HL-C-0129-04","HL-C-0129-05","HL-C-0129-06","HL-C-0129-07"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0129-01","HL-R-0129-02","HL-R-0129-03","HL-R-0129-04","HL-R-0129-05","HL-R-0129-06","HL-R-0129-07","HL-R-0129-08"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NECESSARY","CAUSAL","NEGATION","CONTRAST","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["交友宫"],"star_tags":["紫微"],"transformation_tags":["忌"],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["PARTNERSHIP_NETWORK"],"technique_ids":["HL_ONE_SIX_COMMON_ROOT","HL_SYNC_THREE_LEVEL"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
