{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0144","source_sequence":144,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":525,"source_line_end":528,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四·化忌与财官关系全篇","parent_section":"三、命例详解之一：命宫化忌入官禄，顺行至田宅大限","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(二) 顺行大限追踪（命造顺行大限至田宅宫）\n   大限入田宅宫时，冲宫（夫妻宫）成为大限疾厄宫。疾厄受冲，命\n   难保。\n   此大限十年间，一直会一筹莫展，再努力也是白忙。","raw_text_sha256":"19ab4e4604ad64920d23ee1db69932a65a86e5efe88ea970d18c976a4c56ac20","clause_ids":["HL-C-0144-01","HL-C-0144-02","HL-C-0144-03","HL-C-0144-04","HL-C-0144-05"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0144-01","HL-R-0144-02","HL-R-0144-03"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","SEQUENCE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["夫妻宫","疾厄宫","田宅宫"],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":["大限"],"topic_tags":["MARRIAGE_RELATION","HEALTH_RISK","PROPERTY_HOME"],"technique_ids":["HL_HEALTH"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0145","source_sequence":145,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":530,"source_line_end":539,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四·化忌与财官关系全篇","parent_section":"三、命例详解之一：命宫化忌入官禄，顺行至田宅大限","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   逐流年分析：\n     流年入丑：冲宫成为流年子女宫（合伙宫）。若是合伙事业，这一年\n               就要分家。\n     流年入寅：冲宫成为流年财帛宫。这一年钱财必然受损很大。\n     流年入卯：与大限命宫重叠。这一年会倒店、失业。\n     流年入辰：坐忌。这一年所做的决定，会给日后带来再一次倒店的\n               厄运。\n     流年入巳：冲宫成为流年交友宫。冲交友表示没搞头，青黄不接。\n     流年入午：冲宫成为流年官禄宫。这一年事业败定了。\n     流年入未：冲宫成为流年田宅宫。田宅为财之库，这一年没钱。","raw_text_sha256":"cddc96295f4128b764f0d2523221df94b1c985a792082ded3453cd1e3f49264a","clause_ids":["HL-C-0145-01","HL-C-0145-02","HL-C-0145-03","HL-C-0145-04","HL-C-0145-05","HL-C-0145-06","HL-C-0145-07","HL-C-0145-08","HL-C-0145-09","HL-C-0145-10","HL-C-0145-11","HL-C-0145-12","HL-C-0145-13","HL-C-0145-14","HL-C-0145-15","HL-C-0145-16","HL-C-0145-17"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0145-01","HL-R-0145-02","HL-R-0145-03","HL-R-0145-04","HL-R-0145-05"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","CAUSAL","NEGATION","SEQUENCE"],"palace_tags":["命宫","子女宫","财帛宫","交友宫","官禄宫","田宅宫"],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["禄","忌"],"temporal_tags":["大限","流年"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","FINANCE_CASHFLOW","CHILDREN_FERTILITY","PROPERTY_HOME","PARTNERSHIP_NETWORK"],"technique_ids":["HL_PARTNERSHIP"],"result_term_candidates":["倒店","失业"],"risk_tags":["ENDPOINT_CANDIDATE_ONLY","CATEGORICAL_SOURCE_CLAIM_REQUIRES_CAP"],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0151","source_sequence":151,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":568,"source_line_end":571,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四·化忌与财官关系全篇","parent_section":"四、命例详解之二：甲申年八月卯时生人，命宫在午","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(三) 大限追踪（大限入田宅宫酉宫）\n   大限财帛宫巳宫，天干己，使得武曲化禄入本命财帛宫寅宫。\n   本命财帛宫，丙天干，使得天同化禄入大限官禄宫丑宫。\n   财禄入官：表示投资事业。表面看来，此大限会赚钱。","raw_text_sha256":"ac6476ed20ef312ac619652fe12f1705b1b0cb43307148f7d1f466d4fe69e691","clause_ids":["HL-C-0151-01","HL-C-0151-02","HL-C-0151-03","HL-C-0151-04","HL-C-0151-05"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0151-01","HL-R-0151-02"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CAUSAL","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["财帛宫","官禄宫","田宅宫"],"star_tags":["武曲","天同"],"transformation_tags":["化禄","禄"],"temporal_tags":["本命","大限"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","FINANCE_CASHFLOW","PROPERTY_HOME"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0152","source_sequence":152,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":573,"source_line_end":577,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四·化忌与财官关系全篇","parent_section":"四、命例详解之二：甲申年八月卯时生人，命宫在午","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   然而：\n   财帛宫化忌入官禄宫（寅宫丙廉贞化忌），冲夫妻宫。\n   冲宫（夫妻宫）成为大限疾厄宫。\n   疾厄宫受冲，命难保。\n   → 上述“会赚钱”之判断，已被忌冲疾厄完全破坏。","raw_text_sha256":"816f32c88d4748df49583924224bf3c0572748cf4960df0db809bef3c29f509b","clause_ids":["HL-C-0152-01","HL-C-0152-02","HL-C-0152-03","HL-C-0152-04","HL-C-0152-05"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0152-01"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONTRAST"],"palace_tags":["夫妻宫","财帛宫","疾厄宫","官禄宫"],"star_tags":["廉贞"],"transformation_tags":["化忌","禄","忌"],"temporal_tags":["大限"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","FINANCE_CASHFLOW","MARRIAGE_RELATION","HEALTH_RISK"],"technique_ids":["HL_HEALTH"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
