{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0161","source_sequence":161,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":602,"source_line_end":606,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四·化忌与财官关系全篇","parent_section":"四、命例详解之二：甲申年八月卯时生人，命宫在午","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   四十二岁，流年在丑：冲宫成为流田。田宅为财库，财库受冲会倒店、\n   失业。冲田宅亦表人不在家，坐牢。\n     流年父母宫丙使得廉贞化忌，冲流年田宅。\n     八月十九日，流月在辰，流日在戌。此日命主被法院判刑入狱——\n     侵占土地。","raw_text_sha256":"e384356dc52fbbdd3ffd7f23eef715ba00b138fd61dea5a141df21d5337be0d7","clause_ids":["HL-C-0161-01","HL-C-0161-02","HL-C-0161-03","HL-C-0161-04","HL-C-0161-05","HL-C-0161-06","HL-C-0161-07","HL-C-0161-08"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0161-01","HL-R-0161-02","HL-R-0161-03"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["父母宫"],"star_tags":["廉贞"],"transformation_tags":["化忌","忌"],"temporal_tags":["流年","流月","流日"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","PROPERTY_HOME","PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":["倒店","失业"],"risk_tags":["ENDPOINT_CANDIDATE_ONLY"],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
