{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0168","source_sequence":168,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":631,"source_line_end":633,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四·化忌与财官关系全篇","parent_section":"五、命例详解之三：戊年二月卯时生人，男命，命宫在子","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   三十四岁：流年入大限财帛位。所表现皆与钞票有关，钱脑袋动得勤。\n     冲宫成为流年兄弟位。兄弟为田宅之财帛（生活费）。田宅财帛受冲，\n     生活费常无着落，寅吃卯粮，有时断炊。","raw_text_sha256":"e15c736d6146eef323f549ffd5cd90cc8cd0210da04cc8d664e5afe9e49f6b8a","clause_ids":["HL-C-0168-01","HL-C-0168-02","HL-C-0168-03","HL-C-0168-04","HL-C-0168-05","HL-C-0168-06"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0168-01","HL-R-0168-02"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":["大限","流年"],"topic_tags":["FINANCE_CASHFLOW","PROPERTY_HOME","PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0169","source_sequence":169,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":635,"source_line_end":640,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四·化忌与财官关系全篇","parent_section":"五、命例详解之三：戊年二月卯时生人，男命，命宫在子","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   三十五岁：流年与本命重叠，力量加倍。\n     冲宫在流年夫妻位，夫妻缘分薄，聚少离多。\n     忌星入流年交友之兄弟（床位），表有桃花介入。\n     忌星入官禄位，冲动事业，此年较勤劳认真。\n     冲宫在流年田宅之疾厄。第六位破直接损及第一位，财库有损，破财\n     不免，无积蓄。","raw_text_sha256":"94520202c309ff9045c82291f359977037e238fc8cf403e9c73443885527badc","clause_ids":["HL-C-0169-01","HL-C-0169-02","HL-C-0169-03","HL-C-0169-04","HL-C-0169-05","HL-C-0169-06","HL-C-0169-07"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0169-01","HL-R-0169-02","HL-R-0169-03","HL-R-0169-04"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","COMPARISON","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["禄","忌"],"temporal_tags":["本命","流年"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","FINANCE_CASHFLOW","MARRIAGE_RELATION","HEALTH_RISK","PROPERTY_HOME","PARTNERSHIP_NETWORK","PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":["HL_PEACH_BLOSSOM","HL_HEALTH","HL_HOME_FENGSHUI"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0171","source_sequence":171,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":646,"source_line_end":649,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四·化忌与财官关系全篇","parent_section":"五、命例详解之三：戊年二月卯时生人，男命，命宫在子","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   三十七岁：流年入寅。\n     流年福德坐命干忌。命干忌冲流年财帛。\n     冲宫之交友为流年父母。综合考虑，财运很差。\n     夫妻争吵，因缺少面包，不免多怨言。","raw_text_sha256":"90f0c09e9540f584f1f05ad12af31275890b38ad3754266328bf172d33ced578","clause_ids":["HL-C-0171-01","HL-C-0171-02","HL-C-0171-03","HL-C-0171-04","HL-C-0171-05","HL-C-0171-06"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0171-01","HL-R-0171-02"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["忌"],"temporal_tags":["流年"],"topic_tags":["FINANCE_CASHFLOW","MARRIAGE_RELATION","PARTNERSHIP_NETWORK","PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0172","source_sequence":172,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":651,"source_line_end":656,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四·化忌与财官关系全篇","parent_section":"五、命例详解之三：戊年二月卯时生人，男命，命宫在子","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   三十八岁：流年入卯，与大限重叠，好坏力量加倍。\n     冲宫在流年疾厄宫。疾厄为官禄之田宅（生财之处），不可冲。冲则\n     失业、倒店。\n     命主自述：此年整整一年没做生意。年底好友同情捐资十万重起炉灶，\n     全泡汤。\n     此完全符合方外人之发现——最凶的宫位是冲宫的交友宫。","raw_text_sha256":"406ceeb5547688351c0db6afc504b4ae167fa59173756ffa831ecd79c5ebd270","clause_ids":["HL-C-0172-01","HL-C-0172-02","HL-C-0172-03","HL-C-0172-04","HL-C-0172-05","HL-C-0172-06","HL-C-0172-07","HL-C-0172-08","HL-C-0172-09"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0172-01","HL-R-0172-02","HL-R-0172-03"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["疾厄宫","交友宫"],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["禄"],"temporal_tags":["大限","流年"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","HEALTH_RISK","PROPERTY_HOME","PARTNERSHIP_NETWORK"],"technique_ids":["HL_HEALTH"],"result_term_candidates":["倒店","失业"],"risk_tags":["ENDPOINT_CANDIDATE_ONLY"],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0173","source_sequence":173,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":658,"source_line_end":663,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四·化忌与财官关系全篇","parent_section":"五、命例详解之三：戊年二月卯时生人，男命，命宫在子","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   三十九岁：流年入辰，坐忌。\n     命宫干化出之忌，称“痴情忌”。命主把情完完全全投入此宫位，终\n     其一生痴心在此。\n     本造坐忌于本命官禄宫，表此人痴情于事业。这一年对事业极度认真。\n     官禄宫不怕忌星入，忌入官禄表冲动，冲则发。此年命造投资全自动\n     设备之外销工厂。","raw_text_sha256":"553be0011e390f08d3179892380a8525940491ce29e7883f7408ab3e029d9fa6","clause_ids":["HL-C-0173-01","HL-C-0173-02","HL-C-0173-03","HL-C-0173-04","HL-C-0173-05","HL-C-0173-06","HL-C-0173-07","HL-C-0173-08","HL-C-0173-09"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0173-01","HL-R-0173-02","HL-R-0173-03"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","NEGATION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["命宫","官禄宫"],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["禄","忌"],"temporal_tags":["本命","流年"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK"],"technique_ids":["HL_EXPORT"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
