{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0183","source_sequence":183,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":696,"source_line_end":701,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四·化忌与财官关系全篇","parent_section":"六、化忌综合论断法则汇总","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(五) 痴情忌\n   命宫干化出之忌，所落宫位，表示命主将情感完完全全投入此宫位，\n   终其一生痴心在此。\n   大限或流年行至此宫时，痴情特质充分表露。\n   官禄宫坐命干忌，主痴情于事业。忌入官禄主冲动，冲则发，但仍需\n   合参全局吉凶。","raw_text_sha256":"d4c069f40b51a0cae45407dc0fda86e2375701af67f3cc5af3b5b01b873e4713","clause_ids":["HL-C-0183-01","HL-C-0183-02","HL-C-0183-03","HL-C-0183-04","HL-C-0183-05","HL-C-0183-06","HL-C-0183-07"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0183-01","HL-R-0183-02","HL-R-0183-03","HL-R-0183-04"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CAUSAL","CONTRAST","ALTERNATIVE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["命宫","官禄宫"],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["禄","忌"],"temporal_tags":["大限","流年"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0201","source_sequence":201,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":806,"source_line_end":820,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷五·河洛紫微斗数·断行业全篇","parent_section":"四、河洛紫微斗数十八星曜行业总谱","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(六) 廉贞星\n   五行：属丁火，属阴，主静。\n   行业：\n     - 营业状态为门市，而非跑外务。\n     - 精密仪器：电视、电脑、影印机、录影机、电子计算机等，凡带电\n       之精密仪器皆属之。\n       丙年生人操作仪器故障率偏高，因丙干使廉贞化忌。\n       流日逢丙，最好少开车，电子电路组件易出毛病。\n     - 廉贞亦为血，主刀伤流血。\n       会七杀，格局高者可为护士，格局低者为按摩小姐，亦有在菜市场\n       杀鸡鸭者。\n     - 廉贞为艮土，山坡地、旱田、水果园。故亦可从事水果买卖。\n   实例：某饭店老板寻妻，查其流时夫妻宫，宫干为丙，廉贞化忌入\n   酉宫，酉宫组合为廉贞破军。推断其妻可能去了西门市场之猪肉店或\n   水果店。事后追踪，果然如是。","raw_text_sha256":"0a9447022805ddae7f3951ba3402d33affccb270adfc211b6a1e3dc8bc74f351","clause_ids":["HL-C-0201-01","HL-C-0201-02","HL-C-0201-03","HL-C-0201-04","HL-C-0201-05","HL-C-0201-06","HL-C-0201-07","HL-C-0201-08","HL-C-0201-09","HL-C-0201-10","HL-C-0201-11","HL-C-0201-12","HL-C-0201-13","HL-C-0201-14","HL-C-0201-15","HL-C-0201-16","HL-C-0201-17","HL-C-0201-18"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0201-01","HL-R-0201-02","HL-R-0201-03","HL-R-0201-04","HL-R-0201-05","HL-R-0201-06","HL-R-0201-07","HL-R-0201-08","HL-R-0201-09","HL-R-0201-10","HL-R-0201-11"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","CAUSAL","NEGATION","ALTERNATIVE","SEQUENCE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["夫妻宫"],"star_tags":["廉贞","七杀","破军"],"transformation_tags":["化忌","忌"],"temporal_tags":["流日","流时"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","MARRIAGE_RELATION"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0230","source_sequence":230,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":971,"source_line_end":977,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷六·河洛紫微斗数·论进财全篇","parent_section":"四、实例详解：补习班经营者","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"命盘设定：\n  命宫：在子宫，巨门坐守，天干为甲。\n  子女宫：在酉宫，天府坐守，天干为辛。\n  财帛宫：在申宫，无主星（藏气于命宫巨门）。\n  经营模式：补习班，命主只负责上课，不管财务。钱财收支由其妻子\n  经理出纳。\n  大限：顺行，行至辰宫大限。","raw_text_sha256":"b557ee40c34cf676e8af39109e7d4808021d822c742ace2417fcf89db5c06794","clause_ids":["HL-C-0230-01","HL-C-0230-02","HL-C-0230-03","HL-C-0230-04","HL-C-0230-05","HL-C-0230-06","HL-C-0230-07","HL-C-0230-08"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0230-01","HL-R-0230-02","HL-R-0230-03","HL-R-0230-04"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","NEGATION","LIMITATION"],"palace_tags":["命宫","子女宫","财帛宫"],"star_tags":["天府","巨门"],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":["大限"],"topic_tags":["FINANCE_CASHFLOW","CHILDREN_FERTILITY"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0232","source_sequence":232,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":989,"source_line_end":994,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷六·河洛紫微斗数·论进财全篇","parent_section":"四、实例详解：补习班经营者","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(二) 大限进财之兆\n   行至辰宫大限，本命子女宫（酉）成为大限之交友宫。\n   大限交友宫天干辛，使巨门化禄入本命宫。\n   → 大限交友为大限子女之财帛宫（学生的钱财）。\n   → 禄入命，表示学生的钱财我得到。\n   结论：此大限十年财运颇佳。","raw_text_sha256":"f50e9332519f881da12aa45cb27da4dcfefc564509f407182b51c5c469e04699","clause_ids":["HL-C-0232-01","HL-C-0232-02","HL-C-0232-03","HL-C-0232-04","HL-C-0232-05","HL-C-0232-06"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0232-01","HL-R-0232-02"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CAUSAL","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["命宫","子女宫","财帛宫","交友宫"],"star_tags":["巨门"],"transformation_tags":["化禄","禄"],"temporal_tags":["本命","大限"],"topic_tags":["FINANCE_CASHFLOW","CHILDREN_FERTILITY","PARTNERSHIP_NETWORK"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0233","source_sequence":233,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":996,"source_line_end":1004,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷六·河洛紫微斗数·论进财全篇","parent_section":"四、实例详解：补习班经营者","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(三) 流年进财之兆（丑年）\n   流年行至丑宫。\n   禄入之宫位（子宫）成为流年兄弟宫。\n   兄弟宫为：\n     - 财帛宫之田宅宫。\n     - 田宅宫之财帛宫。\n   皆可视为库位。\n   → 禄入流年兄弟宫，为入库。\n   表示丑年大发利市，财运颇佳，家里的生活费用很富足。","raw_text_sha256":"3372b6de2c06c2672d87c051a26a0e89a3c5741e69e4d10b865c2169e5a970f2","clause_ids":["HL-C-0233-01","HL-C-0233-02","HL-C-0233-03","HL-C-0233-04","HL-C-0233-05","HL-C-0233-06","HL-C-0233-07","HL-C-0233-08","HL-C-0233-09"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0233-01","HL-R-0233-02"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CAUSAL","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["兄弟宫","财帛宫","田宅宫"],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["禄"],"temporal_tags":["流年"],"topic_tags":["FINANCE_CASHFLOW","PROPERTY_HOME","PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0234","source_sequence":234,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1006,"source_line_end":1010,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷六·河洛紫微斗数·论进财全篇","parent_section":"四、实例详解：补习班经营者","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   换个角度看：\n     流年在丑，流年夫妻宫在亥。\n     禄入之宫位（子宫）成为流年夫妻宫之父母宫。\n     父母宫是夫妻财帛宫之交友宫，交友有交易、接触、接受之意。\n     因本造由其妻子理财，禄入流年夫妻之父母，视为进财之兆。","raw_text_sha256":"8b892f8c249c7dce37a6e5ffdf3317ac3c0f4bfbfa0885b05625d76a52f09a46","clause_ids":["HL-C-0234-01","HL-C-0234-02","HL-C-0234-03","HL-C-0234-04","HL-C-0234-05"],"relation_ids":[],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["ASSERTION"],"palace_tags":["夫妻宫","财帛宫","交友宫","父母宫"],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["禄"],"temporal_tags":["流年"],"topic_tags":["FINANCE_CASHFLOW","MARRIAGE_RELATION","PARTNERSHIP_NETWORK","PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0235","source_sequence":235,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1012,"source_line_end":1016,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷六·河洛紫微斗数·论进财全篇","parent_section":"四、实例详解：补习班经营者","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(四) 流年进财之兆（寅年）\n   流年行至寅宫。\n   禄入之宫位（子宫）成为流年夫妻宫，财运似不如丑年之佳。\n   然再观：流年交友宫化禄入本命田宅宫，禄入之宫位又是大限兄弟宫。\n   故寅年财运仍是不错。","raw_text_sha256":"05aa3a32ced98fbedbf07ff326455e2d7a616a6126a7720a1560f5c93f68d37a","clause_ids":["HL-C-0235-01","HL-C-0235-02","HL-C-0235-03","HL-C-0235-04","HL-C-0235-05"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0235-01","HL-R-0235-02","HL-R-0235-03","HL-R-0235-04","HL-R-0235-05","HL-R-0235-06"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CAUSAL","NEGATION","COMPARISON","SEQUENCE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["兄弟宫","夫妻宫","交友宫","田宅宫"],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化禄","禄"],"temporal_tags":["本命","大限","流年"],"topic_tags":["FINANCE_CASHFLOW","MARRIAGE_RELATION","PROPERTY_HOME","PARTNERSHIP_NETWORK","PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0236","source_sequence":236,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1018,"source_line_end":1022,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷六·河洛紫微斗数·论进财全篇","parent_section":"四、实例详解：补习班经营者","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(五) 流月进财之兆\n   欲进一步了解哪几个月较好，以化禄之宫位（卯宫）做定点。\n   当流月入卯、辰、未、申、亥、子诸宫时，是财运比较看好的月份。\n   又，斗君所在之宫干，化禄入流年之命、兄、财、田等，同时也表示\n   进财之兆。","raw_text_sha256":"e1419a2ea4e295f5b5f1ad0455476162903192a5e66f08dc2142fafde5e7a970","clause_ids":["HL-C-0236-01","HL-C-0236-02","HL-C-0236-03","HL-C-0236-04","HL-C-0236-05"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0236-01","HL-R-0236-02","HL-R-0236-03","HL-R-0236-04","HL-R-0236-05","HL-R-0236-06"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","CAUSAL","NEGATION","COMPARISON","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化禄","禄"],"temporal_tags":["流年","流月"],"topic_tags":["FINANCE_CASHFLOW"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0330","source_sequence":330,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1492,"source_line_end":1497,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷九·河洛紫微斗数·补遗与纲要篇","parent_section":"一、出国深造之补充辨析","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"格局与四化配合：\n  星情论格局，四化断契机。\n  论命时，先详细看格局何属。南北派以三合定格局，河洛派看本宫对宫。\n  例如：天机太阴在寅申立命，会天马。此命型动得很厉害。若本命迁移\n  再禄入寅申巳亥，更准。\n  设大限迁移再禄入子午卯酉，则此大限很可能跑单帮。","raw_text_sha256":"a440fe0d655faf97f8fac923c597e261295043608d7b563d4b210ef35df0d94f","clause_ids":["HL-C-0330-01","HL-C-0330-02","HL-C-0330-03","HL-C-0330-04","HL-C-0330-05","HL-C-0330-06","HL-C-0330-07","HL-C-0330-08","HL-C-0330-09"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0330-01","HL-R-0330-02","HL-R-0330-03","HL-R-0330-04","HL-R-0330-05","HL-R-0330-06","HL-R-0330-07","HL-R-0330-08","HL-R-0330-09"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","COMPARISON","SEQUENCE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":["天机","太阴","天马"],"transformation_tags":["禄"],"temporal_tags":["本命","大限"],"topic_tags":["MIGRATION_OUTSIDE"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0333","source_sequence":333,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1508,"source_line_end":1511,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷九·河洛紫微斗数·补遗与纲要篇","parent_section":"一、出国深造之补充辨析","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"  流年应期：\n  倘若流年命宫有化忌入子女冲田宅，表今年外出是绝对的。\n  当流月越过冲宫之时，即为成行之时。\n  哪一天走？参本生日是几号，推法比照流日应期法则。","raw_text_sha256":"ede9d1b355ceeb9de45c0e66ab51685324133c03c8053d6647be7ab52a5339db","clause_ids":["HL-C-0333-01","HL-C-0333-02","HL-C-0333-03","HL-C-0333-04","HL-C-0333-05"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0333-01","HL-R-0333-02"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION"],"palace_tags":["命宫"],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化忌","忌"],"temporal_tags":["流年","流月","流日"],"topic_tags":["CHILDREN_FERTILITY","PROPERTY_HOME","MIGRATION_OUTSIDE"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":["CATEGORICAL_SOURCE_CLAIM_REQUIRES_CAP"],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
