{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0379","source_sequence":379,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1680,"source_line_end":1691,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷十一·流派比较与文书宫辨析","parent_section":"一、三大流派之根本区别","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(一) 三合派\n   用小限。\n   重星情：共一百零八颗星，用以断吉凶。\n   三方看格局。\n   有单用小限不用流年者，亦有小限流年并用者。\n   小限与流年之分工：\n     - 小限看迹象。\n     - 流年断实际。\n   例如血光之灾：先要小限有其象，且流年成局，才算条件符合，确定\n   会发生。\n   又，小限主精神，较抽象，故女命重小限。流年为实质的，故男命重\n   流年。","raw_text_sha256":"f9bfcb50c9058f83d11456b4fc6ee95b3d76ab81eda0fdbf35e75f7c79830df3","clause_ids":["HL-C-0379-01","HL-C-0379-02","HL-C-0379-03","HL-C-0379-04","HL-C-0379-05","HL-C-0379-06","HL-C-0379-07","HL-C-0379-08","HL-C-0379-09","HL-C-0379-10","HL-C-0379-11","HL-C-0379-12","HL-C-0379-13"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0379-01","HL-R-0379-02","HL-R-0379-03","HL-R-0379-04","HL-R-0379-05","HL-R-0379-06","HL-R-0379-07","HL-R-0379-08"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CAUSAL","NEGATION","COMPARISON","SEQUENCE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":["流年","小限"],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
