{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0420","source_sequence":420,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1881,"source_line_end":1883,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷十三·原盘与行限交织论","parent_section":"一、命财官三宫气数位之递进关系","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   以上仅择其最具影响力者叙述。事实上，命与财、财与官、官与命，\n   其本宫与气数位之化曜皆须兼参，以寻其纠缠点。\n   一五九宫为三方，第五宫与本宫之间亦会产生外力影响。","raw_text_sha256":"26a1033c531a0109dc82ea3fd1f4fe52f02f7f10bd2321c10391ea0a8066bc46","clause_ids":["HL-C-0420-01","HL-C-0420-02","HL-C-0420-03","HL-C-0420-04"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0420-01","HL-R-0420-02","HL-R-0420-03"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NECESSARY","LIMITATION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":["HL_ONE_NINE_QISHU"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0421","source_sequence":421,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1885,"source_line_end":1893,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷十三·原盘与行限交织论","parent_section":"一、命财官三宫气数位之递进关系","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(二) 快捷论断法\n   为方便论断之快捷利落，通常论命时：\n     - 论财运：以大限财帛宫化曜给本命财帛宫看，以断大限财运之得失。\n     - 论事业：以大限财帛宫化曜给本命官禄宫看，以决大限事业之成败。\n     - 论荣辱：以大限官禄宫化曜给本命命宫看，以定大限之荣辱。\n   其法依旧：\n     - 入父疾线：主光明。\n     - 入兄友线：主成就。\n     - 入三合方：主格局高。","raw_text_sha256":"1f90f4b816ce3603e8635a4b2fc892e43b7a8eb835cb0473eb3408825e0e34b1","clause_ids":["HL-C-0421-01","HL-C-0421-02","HL-C-0421-03","HL-C-0421-04","HL-C-0421-05","HL-C-0421-06","HL-C-0421-07","HL-C-0421-08","HL-C-0421-09"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0421-01"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["命宫","财帛宫","官禄宫"],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["禄"],"temporal_tags":["本命","大限"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","FINANCE_CASHFLOW"],"technique_ids":["HL_PARENT_DISEASE_DOCUMENT_LINE","HL_SIBLING_FRIEND_ACHIEVEMENT_LINE"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
