{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0426","source_sequence":426,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1907,"source_line_end":1911,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷十三·原盘与行限交织论","parent_section":"三、行限损益——命好与运好之辨","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(一) 原盘好而行限不济\n   例如：本官化禄入本父，主光明。\n     表现在第一大限：国小阶段书读得好，很得师长喜爱。\n     惟若第二、三大限，连连大官都化忌入父疾线——表光明失。\n     此乃命好运不好，无济于事。","raw_text_sha256":"9ed34dc665ea8159948742446b9703596519e13df0773d0ec3211279387ce2a3","clause_ids":["HL-C-0426-01","HL-C-0426-02","HL-C-0426-03","HL-C-0426-04","HL-C-0426-05"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0426-01","HL-R-0426-02","HL-R-0426-03","HL-R-0426-04","HL-R-0426-05"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","NEGATION","CONTRAST","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化禄","化忌","禄","忌"],"temporal_tags":["原盘","大限"],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":["HL_PARENT_DISEASE_DOCUMENT_LINE"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0427","source_sequence":427,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1913,"source_line_end":1916,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷十三·原盘与行限交织论","parent_section":"三、行限损益——命好与运好之辨","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(二) 原盘不行而行限好\n   很多人在其命式中，本官根本就没有化曜入父疾、兄友，而其人却\n   成就了大事业。\n   何以故？","raw_text_sha256":"0ab4a0b46729c1371994ba1e366b2cd39dfca72d298d65d4b0163911eadd9007","clause_ids":["HL-C-0427-01","HL-C-0427-02","HL-C-0427-03","HL-C-0427-04"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0427-01","HL-R-0427-02","HL-R-0427-03"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CAUSAL","NEGATION","CONTRAST"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":["原盘"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0428","source_sequence":428,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1918,"source_line_end":1922,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷十三·原盘与行限交织论","parent_section":"三、行限损益——命好与运好之辨","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   孟子曰：天将降大任于斯人也，必先苦其心志，劳其筋骨，饿其体肤，\n   空乏其身，行拂乱其所为。所以动心忍性，增益其所不能。\n   一个有大担当的人，少壮时荷包里经常没钱，吃穿没着落，不管做\n   什么事总不能称心如意。这样反而能激励他的志节，坚韧他的耐力，\n   增长他所欠缺的本领。","raw_text_sha256":"b478dff943c9d8953e0374bd7b8f1ed2a7edda56c4b277b49a477b453aa3c078","clause_ids":["HL-C-0428-01","HL-C-0428-02","HL-C-0428-03","HL-C-0428-04","HL-C-0428-05","HL-C-0428-06","HL-C-0428-07"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0428-01","HL-R-0428-02","HL-R-0428-03","HL-R-0428-04","HL-R-0428-05","HL-R-0428-06","HL-R-0428-07"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","CAUSAL","NEGATION","CONTRAST","SEQUENCE"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
