{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0433","source_sequence":433,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1938,"source_line_end":1940,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷十三·原盘与行限交织论","parent_section":"四、命例详解：某院级首长命造","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   1. 星情层面\n      文昌同度在命宫。天钺在兄弟宫，天魁在交友宫。\n      魁钺入兄友线：表头脑优秀，从事财经工作者。","raw_text_sha256":"9b6f0540a51eba44196c3b37d33d452f14a64aed858f9d9fcdd72c9e50bcd755","clause_ids":["HL-C-0433-01","HL-C-0433-02","HL-C-0433-03","HL-C-0433-04"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0433-01"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["命宫","兄弟宫","交友宫"],"star_tags":["文昌","天魁","天钺"],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","PARTNERSHIP_NETWORK","PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":["HL_SIBLING_FRIEND_ACHIEVEMENT_LINE"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0434","source_sequence":434,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1942,"source_line_end":1947,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷十三·原盘与行限交织论","parent_section":"四、命例详解：某院级首长命造","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   2. 官禄宫四化\n      本官在子，天干为戊。\n      官禄化禄权科：不入本命父疾线，亦不入兄友线。\n      → 表先天运势平平。\n      官禄化忌：天机化忌入田宅宫，冲子女宫。\n      → 子女宫为财帛之父母，对财运产生外力影响，会有财务上的麻烦。","raw_text_sha256":"32ce0c0f4d13cc6d3ba881a5c0f32acc21fa796fbfaed750f367ad13122e293f","clause_ids":["HL-C-0434-01","HL-C-0434-02","HL-C-0434-03","HL-C-0434-04","HL-C-0434-05","HL-C-0434-06"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0434-01","HL-R-0434-02","HL-R-0434-03"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","SEQUENCE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["子女宫","官禄宫","田宅宫"],"star_tags":["天机"],"transformation_tags":["化禄","化忌","禄","权","科","忌"],"temporal_tags":["本命","先天"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","FINANCE_CASHFLOW","CHILDREN_FERTILITY","PROPERTY_HOME","PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":["HL_PARENT_DISEASE_DOCUMENT_LINE","HL_SIBLING_FRIEND_ACHIEVEMENT_LINE"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0435","source_sequence":435,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1949,"source_line_end":1955,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷十三·原盘与行限交织论","parent_section":"四、命例详解：某院级首长命造","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   3. 财帛宫四化\n      财帛宫天干为庚。\n      化禄：使父母宫太阳化禄。对本命父母产生外力影响，有好处。\n      化忌：入兄弟宫，冲交友宫（官禄之父母）。对官禄宫产生直接\n      冲击力。\n      → 不可自设场屋营业，上班较不忌。惟因事业带来之风波仍不可\n      避免。","raw_text_sha256":"e4c636fe64646b8b8e820653f9256e25c6d3ff9805066265026b143bedae2bd5","clause_ids":["HL-C-0435-01","HL-C-0435-02","HL-C-0435-03","HL-C-0435-04","HL-C-0435-05","HL-C-0435-06","HL-C-0435-07","HL-C-0435-08","HL-C-0435-09","HL-C-0435-10"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0435-01","HL-R-0435-02","HL-R-0435-03","HL-R-0435-04","HL-R-0435-05","HL-R-0435-06"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","NEGATION","CONTRAST","COMPARISON","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["兄弟宫","财帛宫","交友宫","官禄宫","父母宫"],"star_tags":["太阳"],"transformation_tags":["化禄","化忌","禄","忌"],"temporal_tags":["本命"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","FINANCE_CASHFLOW","PARTNERSHIP_NETWORK","PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0436","source_sequence":436,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1957,"source_line_end":1962,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷十三·原盘与行限交织论","parent_section":"四、命例详解：某院级首长命造","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   4. 命宫四化\n      命宫干甲。\n      化禄：入财帛宫。禄是情，表对钞票很感兴趣。\n      化忌：入父母宫，冲疾厄宫。\n      → 忌入父母为基层工作者。冲疾厄，疾厄为财之兄弟，冲则没有\n      成就，或成而后破。须详参行限。","raw_text_sha256":"67ad364eaf93f3f822b32567f9b4deacd95f2dd50085b1975a78924821b8dd18","clause_ids":["HL-C-0436-01","HL-C-0436-02","HL-C-0436-03","HL-C-0436-04","HL-C-0436-05","HL-C-0436-06","HL-C-0436-07","HL-C-0436-08","HL-C-0436-09"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0436-01","HL-R-0436-02","HL-R-0436-03","HL-R-0436-04"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NECESSARY","ALTERNATIVE","SEQUENCE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["命宫","财帛宫","疾厄宫","父母宫"],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化禄","化忌","禄","忌"],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","FINANCE_CASHFLOW","HEALTH_RISK","PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":["HL_HEALTH"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0437","source_sequence":437,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1964,"source_line_end":1970,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷十三·原盘与行限交织论","parent_section":"四、命例详解：某院级首长命造","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   5. 原局总评\n      书香人家子弟，优生、智慧。先天背景并不优厚。\n      其成就乃时势造英雄，行限帮忙。\n      夫妻宫壬干，天梁化禄入父母：表配偶对其成就很得力。\n      生年干庚，父母宫太阳化禄：与生俱来走行政、文教路线，前程\n      似锦。\n      总结：成就有，但坎坷不免。","raw_text_sha256":"8908157162e0139038e02ba1fa9456136e25399379c2f7f383e980ef5d95498e","clause_ids":["HL-C-0437-01","HL-C-0437-02","HL-C-0437-03","HL-C-0437-04","HL-C-0437-05","HL-C-0437-06","HL-C-0437-07","HL-C-0437-08"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0437-01","HL-R-0437-02","HL-R-0437-03","HL-R-0437-04","HL-R-0437-05"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","CONTRAST","SEQUENCE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["夫妻宫","父母宫"],"star_tags":["太阳","天梁"],"transformation_tags":["化禄","禄"],"temporal_tags":["先天"],"topic_tags":["MARRIAGE_RELATION","PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
