{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0440","source_sequence":440,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1979,"source_line_end":1985,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷十三·原盘与行限交织论","parent_section":"四、命例详解：某院级首长命造","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"      辨析——禄忌同宫是否为双忌？\n        生年干庚使太阳化禄入父母宫。\n        同时命宫干甲使太阳化忌入同宫。\n        此非双忌。命忌入父母宫，格调低，多是上班族，当一辈子雇员，\n        永远无法升任职员，离职无退休金，只能领公保。\n        但生年禄与命宫忌同缠，情况不同。年干禄有化解命忌之功能。\n        所谓化解，不是抵消，而是拼出来。","raw_text_sha256":"be98301d56dcdd748663c22374d0a3526ed4898168255102313da830e8094616","clause_ids":["HL-C-0440-01","HL-C-0440-02","HL-C-0440-03","HL-C-0440-04","HL-C-0440-05","HL-C-0440-06","HL-C-0440-07","HL-C-0440-08","HL-C-0440-09"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0440-01","HL-R-0440-02","HL-R-0440-03","HL-R-0440-04","HL-R-0440-05","HL-R-0440-06","HL-R-0440-07"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","NEGATION","LIMITATION","CONTRAST"],"palace_tags":["命宫","父母宫"],"star_tags":["太阳"],"transformation_tags":["化禄","化忌","禄","忌"],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0441","source_sequence":441,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1987,"source_line_end":1991,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷十三·原盘与行限交织论","parent_section":"四、命例详解：某院级首长命造","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"      大官（己干）：天梁化科入本父。\n        → 求学态度不是很积极，但求六十分。考试时眼明手快，同学\n        帮忙，老师送分数，尚且顺利过关。\n      命宫干甲化禄入大限父疾线：情况不同。虽然被动，但考前抱佛脚，\n      抱得很踏实。","raw_text_sha256":"b80901429e86427e331d5229e0cba4afec0471757d5422ee485a4c7d3b29e307","clause_ids":["HL-C-0441-01","HL-C-0441-02","HL-C-0441-03","HL-C-0441-04","HL-C-0441-05","HL-C-0441-06","HL-C-0441-07"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0441-01","HL-R-0441-02","HL-R-0441-03","HL-R-0441-04","HL-R-0441-05"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","CONTRAST","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["命宫"],"star_tags":["天梁"],"transformation_tags":["化禄","化科","禄","科"],"temporal_tags":["大限"],"topic_tags":["EDUCATION_EXAM"],"technique_ids":["HL_PARENT_DISEASE_DOCUMENT_LINE","HL_EXAM"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0442","source_sequence":442,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":1993,"source_line_end":2001,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷十三·原盘与行限交织论","parent_section":"四、命例详解：某院级首长命造","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   第三大限（二十二至三十一岁·杀破狼运）：\n      主开创、奔波。\n      命宫化禄入大迁：主出外有贵人。\n      权入大官：可掌权。\n      大官（戊干）：天机化忌入大父。念书机运不好，成为流亡学生。\n      天机为轴，化忌冲大疾，表身体不健康。\n      时代背景：二十二至三十一岁，为民国三十年至三十九年间。此段\n      岁月为抗战中期，经剿匪，至政府迁往台湾次年为止。命主追随\n      蒋介石戎马，在命盘上表露无遗。人间事，一切都在定数中。","raw_text_sha256":"4395fd98150d260f824f9601a6e06b5a2213be3544ced50719691d70f63bb409","clause_ids":["HL-C-0442-01","HL-C-0442-02","HL-C-0442-03","HL-C-0442-04","HL-C-0442-05","HL-C-0442-06","HL-C-0442-07","HL-C-0442-08","HL-C-0442-09","HL-C-0442-10","HL-C-0442-11","HL-C-0442-12","HL-C-0442-13"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0442-01","HL-R-0442-02","HL-R-0442-03","HL-R-0442-04","HL-R-0442-05"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["命宫"],"star_tags":["天机"],"transformation_tags":["化禄","化忌","禄","权","忌"],"temporal_tags":["大限"],"topic_tags":["HEALTH_RISK"],"technique_ids":["HL_HEALTH"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
