{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0643","source_sequence":643,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2809,"source_line_end":2816,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"三、命例详解之一：宗师格局·事业好变动","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(二) 命宫在子之特性\n   子为一阳动。凡命宫在子者，一般比较会开创，是各行各业之领袖\n   人物。\n   点子特别多，喜欢搞发明。就其所从事之行业，能创新，能开风气\n   之先。\n   由于肯不断努力，会提升自己之社会地位。\n   即使流年犯指背，骂他的人也不敢正面乱叫。此乃上天给命宫在子\n   之人一点温馨之处。","raw_text_sha256":"e67ae8a1ded80f03f173dd2cc99248f3357ce51f4844369861b93f7253bb2f19","clause_ids":["HL-C-0643-01","HL-C-0643-02","HL-C-0643-03","HL-C-0643-04","HL-C-0643-05","HL-C-0643-06","HL-C-0643-07","HL-C-0643-08","HL-C-0643-09","HL-C-0643-10","HL-C-0643-11"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0643-01","HL-R-0643-02","HL-R-0643-03","HL-R-0643-04","HL-R-0643-05","HL-R-0643-06"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","CAUSAL","NEGATION","COMPARISON","SEQUENCE"],"palace_tags":["命宫"],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":["流年"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0644","source_sequence":644,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2818,"source_line_end":2822,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"三、命例详解之一：宗师格局·事业好变动","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   另方面，命宫在子之人也很可怜。\n   他永远是种苹果的李老先生（小学课本之课文），播种是为后代。\n   套用俗话：这种人就是打天下的陈友谅。好处永远轮不到自己。\n   常常是辛苦开创的局面，由于财力不继或某种因素，不得已拱手让人。\n   即：辛苦得来，落入外人之家。","raw_text_sha256":"74118ddd1c26d8fd11355470c33c6cdaa99240d4a82282bd7582d1244c871cbc","clause_ids":["HL-C-0644-01","HL-C-0644-02","HL-C-0644-03","HL-C-0644-04","HL-C-0644-05","HL-C-0644-06"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0644-01","HL-R-0644-02","HL-R-0644-03","HL-R-0644-04","HL-R-0644-05","HL-R-0644-06"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CAUSAL","NEGATION","LIMITATION","ALTERNATIVE","SEQUENCE"],"palace_tags":["命宫"],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0645","source_sequence":645,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2824,"source_line_end":2826,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"三、命例详解之一：宗师格局·事业好变动","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(三) 宗师格局\n   申宫在迁移，天机化忌。\n   凡命身在子午线，有天机化忌者，为发明家、为宗师之格局。","raw_text_sha256":"43f0758c48e119a4e3a6f72522ca3ae1a2e5c3ab152de6bb19e26b19af85b7b4","clause_ids":["HL-C-0645-01","HL-C-0645-02","HL-C-0645-03"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0645-01","HL-R-0645-02"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":["天机"],"transformation_tags":["化忌","忌"],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["MIGRATION_OUTSIDE"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
