{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0647","source_sequence":647,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2832,"source_line_end":2836,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"三、命例详解之一：宗师格局·事业好变动","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(四) 宗师之叹\n   佛陀为一代宗师，放弃王子尊荣，苦修林中三年。疲极下山，接受\n   牧羊女鲜奶。比丘因此离去。后坐化菩提树下，发誓若不彻悟大道\n   愿死树下。修行过程苦不堪言。证道后四处说法，收取微薄资财，\n   顶多沿门托钵，意在使信众因布施积攒善缘。其悲心何其浩荡。","raw_text_sha256":"5312d7b2629ca8a1b4eadb055337cf114e6762920cfcc82a4bbf45b227415bcd","clause_ids":["HL-C-0647-01","HL-C-0647-02","HL-C-0647-03","HL-C-0647-04","HL-C-0647-05","HL-C-0647-06","HL-C-0647-07","HL-C-0647-08","HL-C-0647-09","HL-C-0647-10","HL-C-0647-11"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0647-01","HL-R-0647-02","HL-R-0647-03","HL-R-0647-04","HL-R-0647-05","HL-R-0647-06","HL-R-0647-07","HL-R-0647-08"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","NEGATION","SEQUENCE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0648","source_sequence":648,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2838,"source_line_end":2839,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"三、命例详解之一：宗师格局·事业好变动","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   耶稣亦是宗师，受政治迫害，流离沙漠接受魔鬼试炼四十九天。后\n   被钉上十字架。","raw_text_sha256":"2599565fa6ec3e182168a0bcfcb3b52c381c12c37af794a186d6b0367f889791","clause_ids":["HL-C-0648-01","HL-C-0648-02","HL-C-0648-03"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0648-01","HL-R-0648-02","HL-R-0648-03"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["SEQUENCE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["SPIRITUAL_CULTURAL"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":["SPIRITUAL_LITERALIZATION_PROHIBITED"],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":true}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0649","source_sequence":649,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2841,"source_line_end":2844,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"三、命例详解之一：宗师格局·事业好变动","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   孔子亦是宗师，周游列国，花子贡之钱，自身穷困。年纪大了回家\n   教学，私下无立案。招生困难，以干肉充当学费。终其一生仅三千\n   子弟。家庭亦不美满，儿子早夭，媳妇不明事理，故有“女子难养，\n   近之不逊，远之则怨”之叹。","raw_text_sha256":"a3f5f52357f7b0718fd23455a61e6dc651b8693244ccd3ac3946411df0e56c18","clause_ids":["HL-C-0649-01","HL-C-0649-02","HL-C-0649-03","HL-C-0649-04","HL-C-0649-05","HL-C-0649-06","HL-C-0649-07","HL-C-0649-08"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0649-01","HL-R-0649-02","HL-R-0649-03","HL-R-0649-04","HL-R-0649-05","HL-R-0649-06","HL-R-0649-07"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","CAUSAL","NEGATION","LIMITATION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":["早夭"],"risk_tags":["ENDPOINT_CANDIDATE_ONLY","EXTREME_ENDPOINT_LIMIT"],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":true}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0650","source_sequence":650,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2846,"source_line_end":2848,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"三、命例详解之一：宗师格局·事业好变动","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   宗师是人间最忌讳之事。一件件事降临头上，生不如死，一筹莫展，\n   而后困而知之，以自己痛苦之经历作为人类之里程碑。\n   宗师是乘愿而来之菩萨，是环境磨练出来的，不是自封的。","raw_text_sha256":"fa75105f7ceec8947191b1a166690edcc5bf2faacaff2c4e18b331d56e841897","clause_ids":["HL-C-0650-01","HL-C-0650-02","HL-C-0650-03","HL-C-0650-04"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0650-01","HL-R-0650-02","HL-R-0650-03","HL-R-0650-04"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","COMPARISON","SEQUENCE"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["忌"],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0651","source_sequence":651,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2850,"source_line_end":2857,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"三、命例详解之一：宗师格局·事业好变动","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(五) 星情分析\n   命宫在子坐巨门。\n   官禄宫在辰，必有太阳。\n     太阳为丙火，从寅上起长生，辰为冠带位。\n     冠带之太阳够亮（上午七至九时），喜欢表现，有爱心。\n   命宫巨门为长舌妇，爱讲话。\n   → 太阳巨门组合：适合当老师、民意代表、商务代表等。\n   命宫巨门亦是赤脚仙，可能学算命，会端罗盘。","raw_text_sha256":"772de48ff05bb6ab4b06e083e446ecc7e3b5dcb82c8c573a2a47d31d86ea4a58","clause_ids":["HL-C-0651-01","HL-C-0651-02","HL-C-0651-03","HL-C-0651-04","HL-C-0651-05","HL-C-0651-06","HL-C-0651-07","HL-C-0651-08"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0651-01","HL-R-0651-02","HL-R-0651-03"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["命宫","官禄宫"],"star_tags":["太阳","巨门"],"transformation_tags":["禄"],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0652","source_sequence":652,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2859,"source_line_end":2864,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"三、命例详解之一：宗师格局·事业好变动","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(六) 大限与流年事业变动追踪\n   阳男顺行，第四大限（34-43岁）入卯位。\n   大官在未，天干己，使得武曲化禄入卯位。\n   卯位乙干转太阴化忌入戌宫，冲辰宫。\n   当35岁流年入子位，冲宫（戌冲辰）成为流年官禄宫。\n   → 大官之禄转忌冲流官，主事业有好的变动。","raw_text_sha256":"079b4fb011d75080a08c8e9fc57700f4da225a618e0948b1654a0e33c7dc2c40","clause_ids":["HL-C-0652-01","HL-C-0652-02","HL-C-0652-03","HL-C-0652-04","HL-C-0652-05","HL-C-0652-06"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0652-01","HL-R-0652-02","HL-R-0652-03","HL-R-0652-04","HL-R-0652-05"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","NEGATION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["官禄宫"],"star_tags":["武曲","太阴"],"transformation_tags":["化禄","化忌","禄","忌"],"temporal_tags":["大限","流年"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
