{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0654","source_sequence":654,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2869,"source_line_end":2876,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"三、命例详解之一：宗师格局·事业好变动","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(七) 好变动之含义\n   事业好的变动，如：\n     职务调升。\n     转换工作单位。\n     不一定是彻底改行。\n     若为店面生意，可能是重新装修或增加营业项目。\n     若为厂商，可能扩充营业网之类。\n     当然，改行换工作亦包含在内。","raw_text_sha256":"aeb742f86c08ecf9dc3793d2e2ef8e7d52d080d554a7b5a60342b3ad0c28b7de","clause_ids":["HL-C-0654-01","HL-C-0654-02","HL-C-0654-03","HL-C-0654-04","HL-C-0654-05","HL-C-0654-06","HL-C-0654-07","HL-C-0654-08"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0654-01","HL-R-0654-02","HL-R-0654-03","HL-R-0654-04","HL-R-0654-05","HL-R-0654-06"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","NEGATION","ALTERNATIVE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":["CATEGORICAL_SOURCE_CLAIM_REQUIRES_CAP"],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
