{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0656","source_sequence":656,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2880,"source_line_end":2882,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"四、命例详解之二：雄宿乾元格·事业变动","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(一) 基本信息\n   生年：丙申年五月辰时，男命。\n   命宫：在寅，廉贞坐命。","raw_text_sha256":"d32449cf9ab22c0797a290af26f3fa0556b4728f10b44a032c42f0260b1ba1bb","clause_ids":["HL-C-0656-01","HL-C-0656-02","HL-C-0656-03"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0656-01"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["命宫"],"star_tags":["廉贞"],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0657","source_sequence":657,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2884,"source_line_end":2888,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"四、命例详解之二：雄宿乾元格·事业变动","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(二) 格局分析\n   廉贞在寅申二宫，为“雄宿乾元格”。\n   赋文云：“一鸣惊人”。\n   → 意为晨鸡一唱，白天一整天却默不作声。\n   → 故雄宿乾元之成就，不能持续有恒。","raw_text_sha256":"9a0aa8cf890cf4d26517bc197cd54865fdfc965fa94d9933dfca68f729189113","clause_ids":["HL-C-0657-01","HL-C-0657-02","HL-C-0657-03","HL-C-0657-04","HL-C-0657-05"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0657-01","HL-R-0657-02","HL-R-0657-03","HL-R-0657-04"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CAUSAL","NEGATION","CONTRAST"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":["廉贞"],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0658","source_sequence":658,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2890,"source_line_end":2891,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"四、命例详解之二：雄宿乾元格·事业变动","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   某师兄廉贞在申坐命，因看好魔术方块及时赚了很多钱。后野心大了，\n   再投资更大笔，导致血本无归还负债。此即雄宿乾元之写照。","raw_text_sha256":"f2115911d78f6729a5e1ffb0ec61e2bba2b1925f24b353971ba1a0ba719824de","clause_ids":["HL-C-0658-01","HL-C-0658-02","HL-C-0658-03","HL-C-0658-04"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0658-01","HL-R-0658-02","HL-R-0658-03","HL-R-0658-04"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","COMPARISON","SEQUENCE"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":["廉贞"],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0659","source_sequence":659,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2893,"source_line_end":2897,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"四、命例详解之二：雄宿乾元格·事业变动","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   廉贞在寅申，对宫必有贪狼来照。\n   贪狼为食禄之星，一生不免多酒色财气。\n   女命感情多波折。\n   流日走到贪狼对宫，这一天人请客；入贪狼位我请人。颇准。合参\n   禄忌谁请客更验。","raw_text_sha256":"f905cb5bdb12968655148c98f3c90a0adf77226b87f72b392448e41983dff934","clause_ids":["HL-C-0659-01","HL-C-0659-02","HL-C-0659-03","HL-C-0659-04","HL-C-0659-05","HL-C-0659-06","HL-C-0659-07","HL-C-0659-08"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0659-01","HL-R-0659-02"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","COMPARISON"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":["廉贞","贪狼"],"transformation_tags":["禄","忌"],"temporal_tags":["流日"],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0660","source_sequence":660,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2899,"source_line_end":2903,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"四、命例详解之二：雄宿乾元格·事业变动","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(三) 婚姻提示\n   本造夫妻宫坐七杀，必然常吵架。\n   杀破狼是开创之格局，什么事都好开创，唯有夫妻事不能多开创。多\n   开创则杜鹃窝覆巢。\n   凡命成杀破狼局，或夫妻位杀破狼局，皆表婚姻不美。","raw_text_sha256":"2dd6e7c1a255cc297bf7a49f1ebb298c7d90e75b2cb5cab281582bd3c9e28fdd","clause_ids":["HL-C-0660-01","HL-C-0660-02","HL-C-0660-03","HL-C-0660-04","HL-C-0660-05","HL-C-0660-06"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0660-01","HL-R-0660-02","HL-R-0660-03","HL-R-0660-04","HL-R-0660-05","HL-R-0660-06","HL-R-0660-07"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","NEGATION","CONTRAST","ALTERNATIVE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["夫妻宫"],"star_tags":["七杀"],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["MARRIAGE_RELATION"],"technique_ids":["HL_MARRIAGE"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":["CATEGORICAL_SOURCE_CLAIM_REQUIRES_CAP"],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0661","source_sequence":661,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2905,"source_line_end":2910,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"四、命例详解之二：雄宿乾元格·事业变动","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(四) 大限与流年事业变动追踪\n   第三大限在辰。\n   大官在申，天干丙，使得天同化禄入巳宫。\n   巳宫天干癸，使得贪狼化忌转入申宫，冲寅宫。\n   当27岁流年入戌，冲宫成为流年官禄宫。\n   → 大官之禄转忌冲流官，主事业变动。","raw_text_sha256":"d299f38fa6a4fdefa23d33399a2702d4edabb834b875759568490b96168d88da","clause_ids":["HL-C-0661-01","HL-C-0661-02","HL-C-0661-03","HL-C-0661-04","HL-C-0661-05","HL-C-0661-06"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0661-01","HL-R-0661-02","HL-R-0661-03","HL-R-0661-04"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["官禄宫"],"star_tags":["天同","贪狼"],"transformation_tags":["化禄","化忌","禄","忌"],"temporal_tags":["大限","流年"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
