{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0665","source_sequence":665,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2923,"source_line_end":2929,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"五、命例详解之三：日月守命·钱财建设性花费","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(二) 走名走利之判断\n   通常一人一生，到底是走名之路线，或走利之路线，或可名利双收\n   之格局，除了以化曜去决定外，亦须星情合参。\n   一般情况：\n     机月同梁格：一生较为平顺，宜走名之路线。\n     杀破狼格局：走利之路线。\n     日月守命在丑：可名利双收。本造即此格。","raw_text_sha256":"9379f2ea48eead91f203615a41054909fdc4ff2306a86cb91a4e6b3b0da81090","clause_ids":["HL-C-0665-01","HL-C-0665-02","HL-C-0665-03","HL-C-0665-04","HL-C-0665-05","HL-C-0665-06","HL-C-0665-07","HL-C-0665-08"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0665-01","HL-R-0665-02","HL-R-0665-03"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NECESSARY","ALTERNATIVE","COMPARISON"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0666","source_sequence":666,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2931,"source_line_end":2937,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"五、命例详解之三：日月守命·钱财建设性花费","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(三) 大限与流年钱财变动追踪\n   阳男走顺行大限。\n   第四大限入辰。\n   大财在子宫，宫干甲化禄入申宫。\n   申宫干庚转忌入亥宫，冲巳宫。\n   当34岁流年入酉，冲宫（亥冲巳）成为流年财帛宫。\n   → 大财之禄转忌冲流财，表此年用钱多，为建设性花费。","raw_text_sha256":"333ff43a0444816e29a0a06f369404ab363997122ca3d883655b9a597b3b1dec","clause_ids":["HL-C-0666-01","HL-C-0666-02","HL-C-0666-03","HL-C-0666-04","HL-C-0666-05","HL-C-0666-06","HL-C-0666-07"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0666-01","HL-R-0666-02","HL-R-0666-03","HL-R-0666-04","HL-R-0666-05"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["财帛宫"],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化禄","禄","忌"],"temporal_tags":["大限","流年"],"topic_tags":["FINANCE_CASHFLOW"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
