{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0671","source_sequence":671,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":2953,"source_line_end":2956,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十二·流年事业与钱财变动应期","parent_section":"六、技法总结：禄转忌与忌追忌流年应期","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(三) 附注\n   “转忌”者，化禄入某宫，再以该宫之干化忌，转冲目标宫位。\n   “追忌”者，化忌入某宫，再以该宫之干化忌，追冲目标宫位。\n   此为河洛紫微斗数流年应期之快捷断法。","raw_text_sha256":"c0863340d60856fbc721fd6587356f87c52bbe8d08026d54213b9044ecd2e8a4","clause_ids":["HL-C-0671-01","HL-C-0671-02","HL-C-0671-03","HL-C-0671-04"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0671-01","HL-R-0671-02","HL-R-0671-03"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["SEQUENCE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":["紫微"],"transformation_tags":["化禄","化忌","禄","忌"],"temporal_tags":["流年"],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
