{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0783","source_sequence":783,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":3451,"source_line_end":3457,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷二十五·结婚限年诀窍全篇","parent_section":"六、命例详解之三：丙戌年十二月卯时生女命","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"     第四大限：\n       33-42岁大限夫妻宫癸干，贪狼化忌入寅。大夫与大疾相紧。\n       当流年入未，大夫之忌与流疾重叠。此年暗度陈仓。\n       大限乙干紫微化科入辰照戌。\n       37岁流年入科照之地。有情人终成眷属，共营正常之婚姻生活。\n       惟户籍登记仍以同居为宜。\n       因夫妻宫与大限文书宫重叠，丙廉贞自化忌出之故。","raw_text_sha256":"5c3870ff12ed7a8c76a0900f4701add14a2eaf842b33bfcabf76e85fbaceafee","clause_ids":["HL-C-0783-01","HL-C-0783-02","HL-C-0783-03","HL-C-0783-04","HL-C-0783-05","HL-C-0783-06","HL-C-0783-07","HL-C-0783-08","HL-C-0783-09","HL-C-0783-10"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0783-01","HL-R-0783-02","HL-R-0783-03","HL-R-0783-04","HL-R-0783-05","HL-R-0783-06","HL-R-0783-07"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","CAUSAL","NEGATION","CONTRAST","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["夫妻宫"],"star_tags":["紫微","廉贞","贪狼"],"transformation_tags":["化科","化忌","自化忌","科","忌"],"temporal_tags":["大限","流年"],"topic_tags":["MARRIAGE_RELATION","EDUCATION_EXAM","LEGAL_DOCUMENT"],"technique_ids":["HL_SELF_TRANSFORM","HL_MARRIAGE"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"ZERO_CASE_DEMO","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
