{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-0988","source_sequence":988,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":4479,"source_line_end":4487,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷三十一·紫微斗数·事业格局与禄忌双忌辨析","parent_section":"第一篇：命禄入线与发展路线","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(三) 小限派与流年派之辨析\n   师兄走小限派、三合派。\n   小限是抽象的，流年是实质的。\n   古代社会，贫富、贵贱悬殊，社会流动性小，精神重于物质。用小限\n   断，合理。\n   今日社会平等，职业不分贵贱，人人就业机会均等，打拼就有。因此\n   流年重于小限。\n   看流年以下之盘（含年、月、日、时），看本宫对宫就可以，不必看\n   三方。","raw_text_sha256":"2cfb7e38f6a7a58af687217d632f7213dda280917c943b649294e8371aa12cde","clause_ids":["HL-C-0988-01","HL-C-0988-02","HL-C-0988-03","HL-C-0988-04","HL-C-0988-05","HL-C-0988-06","HL-C-0988-07","HL-C-0988-08","HL-C-0988-09","HL-C-0988-10","HL-C-0988-11"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-0988-01","HL-R-0988-02","HL-R-0988-03","HL-R-0988-04","HL-R-0988-05"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":["流年","小限"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
