{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-1436","source_sequence":1436,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":6326,"source_line_end":6329,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四十三·十二宫象意与杂断法则补遗","parent_section":"第二篇：同类不忌与自化法则","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(一) 同类不忌法则\n   命、限、年盘之十二宫化忌，入同类宫位叫“同类归档不忌”。\n   如大限官禄化忌入流年官禄，为化忌不忌（同类相入，忌不为祸）。\n   如大限疾厄化忌入本命疾厄，亦为不忌。","raw_text_sha256":"34a8f1a3d6d15d18380402f105d2521715f2b134ac6f42f1ca1a504dab0441de","clause_ids":["HL-C-1436-01","HL-C-1436-02","HL-C-1436-03","HL-C-1436-04"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-1436-01","HL-R-1436-02","HL-R-1436-03","HL-R-1436-04","HL-R-1436-05"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化忌","禄","忌"],"temporal_tags":["本命","大限","流年"],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","HEALTH_RISK"],"technique_ids":["HL_HEALTH","HL_RELATIVE_GOOD_BAD"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
