{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-1612","source_sequence":1612,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":7270,"source_line_end":7276,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四十七·紫微斗数·一六共宗与终极口诀汇编","parent_section":"四、进财与购屋正论","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"田宅不可自化忌，田宅化忌不可入迁移冲命，表与家族缘薄，与房地产\n无缘。\n生年忌在田宅，当大限行抵田宅位时，表田宅会有变动。\n大限之田宅化忌冲本田，且禄权科不照，表不能买房子。若忌冲而禄权科\n有照，要流年越过忌以后才有。\n忌入田宅：表买房子钱不够。\n禄照田宅：表买新房子。权照田宅：为翻新房子。","raw_text_sha256":"a189fad9090329eda082dda2c4bcb7f3f2ac950f119c153f809494bc0c00c54e","clause_ids":["HL-C-1612-01","HL-C-1612-02","HL-C-1612-03","HL-C-1612-04","HL-C-1612-05","HL-C-1612-06","HL-C-1612-07","HL-C-1612-08","HL-C-1612-09"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-1612-01","HL-R-1612-02","HL-R-1612-03","HL-R-1612-04","HL-R-1612-05","HL-R-1612-06","HL-R-1612-07"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","NEGATION","SEQUENCE"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化忌","自化忌","禄","权","科","忌"],"temporal_tags":["大限","流年"],"topic_tags":["PROPERTY_HOME","MIGRATION_OUTSIDE"],"technique_ids":["HL_SELF_TRANSFORM"],"result_term_candidates":["买房"],"risk_tags":["ENDPOINT_CANDIDATE_ONLY"],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
