{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-1653","source_sequence":1653,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":7461,"source_line_end":7468,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四十八·紫微斗数·终极理则与大限流年应验全篇","parent_section":"二、十二宫吉凶根本断法","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(一) 命格速断\n   命会权禄：为生意人。\n   命会权科：为上班族。\n   官之忌入父疾线：表一生际遇很差。\n   官之忌入兄友线：表一生容易犯小人。\n   官之禄权科入父疾线：表一生际遇不错。\n   官之禄权科入兄友线：表一生很有成就。\n   命财官化禄权科入子田线、父疾线：皆表一生际遇不错。","raw_text_sha256":"96d6b481c13402e0228fe94856b56430c12b87a2b951e188d6868e9dbd1cc8ca","clause_ids":["HL-C-1653-01","HL-C-1653-02","HL-C-1653-03","HL-C-1653-04","HL-C-1653-05","HL-C-1653-06","HL-C-1653-07","HL-C-1653-08"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-1653-01","HL-R-1653-02"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化禄","禄","权","科","忌"],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":["HL_PARENT_DISEASE_DOCUMENT_LINE","HL_SIBLING_FRIEND_ACHIEVEMENT_LINE","HL_CHILD_PROPERTY_LINE"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
