{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-1658","source_sequence":1658,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":7484,"source_line_end":7487,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四十八·紫微斗数·终极理则与大限流年应验全篇","parent_section":"三、禄权科忌与财运正论","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(二) 财帛化曜去向新解\n   财帛化禄入命：是说钱我自己花，非进财。\n   财帛化禄入官禄：表投资事业，或投资在学业上。\n   财帛化禄入兄友线、父疾线：视为好现象。","raw_text_sha256":"c46b1ea29c620b5775e8ae27dc96207dea368a082ceecb7413ce5a071a46f93c","clause_ids":["HL-C-1658-01","HL-C-1658-02","HL-C-1658-03","HL-C-1658-04"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-1658-01","HL-R-1658-02"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","ALTERNATIVE"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化禄","禄"],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","FINANCE_CASHFLOW"],"technique_ids":["HL_PARENT_DISEASE_DOCUMENT_LINE","HL_SIBLING_FRIEND_ACHIEVEMENT_LINE"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-1659","source_sequence":1659,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":7489,"source_line_end":7493,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四十八·紫微斗数·终极理则与大限流年应验全篇","parent_section":"三、禄权科忌与财运正论","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   财帛化禄入父母（交友之财帛）：表我把钱财给人。试想什么情况我把\n   钱给人？必然是我得到你的好处，我才把钱给你。例如你把货给我，我支付\n   价款；或你帮我工作，我给你工资。财帛化禄入父母就照疾厄，疾厄为官禄\n   之田宅（生财场屋），即我把钱给朋友，朋友得了我的钱财，就照顾我的\n   生意（禄照疾厄）。余类推。","raw_text_sha256":"36dec749c733dce00a70f2d18fe34bd6a3e95b1175d445a87ec725a07c36e155","clause_ids":["HL-C-1659-01","HL-C-1659-02","HL-C-1659-03","HL-C-1659-04","HL-C-1659-05","HL-C-1659-06","HL-C-1659-07","HL-C-1659-08","HL-C-1659-09","HL-C-1659-10","HL-C-1659-11"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-1659-01"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["ALTERNATIVE"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化禄","禄"],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","FINANCE_CASHFLOW","HEALTH_RISK","PROPERTY_HOME","PARTNERSHIP_NETWORK","PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":["HL_HEALTH"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":["CATEGORICAL_SOURCE_CLAIM_REQUIRES_CAP"],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-1660","source_sequence":1660,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":7495,"source_line_end":7498,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四十八·紫微斗数·终极理则与大限流年应验全篇","parent_section":"三、禄权科忌与财运正论","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(三) 进财真诀\n   进财是看“疾厄”化禄入什么宫位来断。疾厄为官禄之田宅，是生财之地。\n   如何支配钱财：是看“财帛”化禄入什么宫位来断。我方禄入我方，只在\n   判断如何支配钱财。","raw_text_sha256":"4c460aef1ea4cf85ae7784d3bf1da69483fbf4b88ffa9057c62de845259126ba","clause_ids":["HL-C-1660-01","HL-C-1660-02","HL-C-1660-03","HL-C-1660-04","HL-C-1660-05","HL-C-1660-06"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-1660-01","HL-R-1660-02"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["LIMITATION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化禄","禄"],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","FINANCE_CASHFLOW","HEALTH_RISK","PROPERTY_HOME"],"technique_ids":["HL_SELF_OTHER_PALACE","HL_HEALTH"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-1661","source_sequence":1661,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":7500,"source_line_end":7505,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四十八·紫微斗数·终极理则与大限流年应验全篇","parent_section":"三、禄权科忌与财运正论","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(四) 财运分判法则\n   今年财运如何？看大限疾厄化禄入流年之何宫：\n     禄入流田：可能买房子，或储蓄起来。\n     禄入父母：为存入银行。\n     禄入兄弟：表家用不缺。\n     入夫妻：也表购房。","raw_text_sha256":"da21f141243cd8fe8cb98e86b68ca67d3404392b5cbb607afe76a036051b78af","clause_ids":["HL-C-1661-01","HL-C-1661-02","HL-C-1661-03","HL-C-1661-04","HL-C-1661-05","HL-C-1661-06","HL-C-1661-07"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-1661-01","HL-R-1661-02","HL-R-1661-03"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","ALTERNATIVE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化禄","禄"],"temporal_tags":["大限","流年"],"topic_tags":["FINANCE_CASHFLOW","MARRIAGE_RELATION","HEALTH_RISK","PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":["HL_HEALTH"],"result_term_candidates":["买房"],"risk_tags":["ENDPOINT_CANDIDATE_ONLY"],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-1662","source_sequence":1662,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":7507,"source_line_end":7516,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四十八·紫微斗数·终极理则与大限流年应验全篇","parent_section":"三、禄权科忌与财运正论","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(五) 财星吉凶详解\n   财帛化禄入夫妻，化忌入交友：为所赚钱财最后一文不剩。\n   财帛化禄入父母，化忌入田宅：比较不会被倒。财帛入田宅不为忌，冲\n   田宅则为破库。\n   财帛忌入福德：表有钱没钱都要享受，赚多少花多少，一生过路财神。\n     若福德有生年科：为很有得享，且能量入为出。\n     若福德有生年禄：表无财。\n     若福德有生年权：是想赚钱，此生年权有制止享受之功能。\n   生年忌在财帛，福德再飞忌入为水忌，以吉论，可经营大规模事业。其余\n   命迁线、夫官线有上述情况同论。","raw_text_sha256":"dd2563f9c2621123db7756acc2896daa3278e7b6d32c46a3b868872bdd229043","clause_ids":["HL-C-1662-01","HL-C-1662-02","HL-C-1662-03","HL-C-1662-04","HL-C-1662-05","HL-C-1662-06","HL-C-1662-07","HL-C-1662-08","HL-C-1662-09","HL-C-1662-10","HL-C-1662-11","HL-C-1662-12"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-1662-01","HL-R-1662-02","HL-R-1662-03","HL-R-1662-04","HL-R-1662-05","HL-R-1662-06","HL-R-1662-07","HL-R-1662-08","HL-R-1662-09","HL-R-1662-10","HL-R-1662-11"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","NEGATION","COMPARISON","SEQUENCE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化禄","化忌","禄","权","科","忌"],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","FINANCE_CASHFLOW","MARRIAGE_RELATION","PROPERTY_HOME","PARTNERSHIP_NETWORK","PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-1663","source_sequence":1663,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":7518,"source_line_end":7521,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四十八·紫微斗数·终极理则与大限流年应验全篇","parent_section":"三、禄权科忌与财运正论","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(六) 丙年生人命格定位\n   丙年生人，得视丙位于何宫，就以该宫来断命格。\n   丙在福德，设使得廉贞化忌入子女冲田宅，则表示失财。\n   丙年生人，命宫为丙，化忌入福德，则显示此造好吃懒做。","raw_text_sha256":"db6cc7a4f4a7e74344abbc657d1ffedc4066e5d9d3f3caee5133e32de52e6eef","clause_ids":["HL-C-1663-01","HL-C-1663-02","HL-C-1663-03","HL-C-1663-04"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-1663-01","HL-R-1663-02","HL-R-1663-03"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","CAUSAL","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["命宫"],"star_tags":["廉贞"],"transformation_tags":["化忌","忌"],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["CHILDREN_FERTILITY","PROPERTY_HOME"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
