{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-1667","source_sequence":1667,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":7533,"source_line_end":7537,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四十八·紫微斗数·终极理则与大限流年应验全篇","parent_section":"五、我方与他方之损益论","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(一) 我宫定义\n   我宫（我方）：命宫、兄弟宫、财帛宫、疾厄宫、官禄宫、田宅宫。\n   命与疾厄为我之一六位。财帛与田宅为财帛之一六位。官禄与兄弟为事业\n   之一六位。\n   其余宫位视为他方，表别人的宫位。","raw_text_sha256":"eb33c1e6202c1e8e12109de57c829f068bf1e5dec03a7630fb2deddd05f167cf","clause_ids":["HL-C-1667-01","HL-C-1667-02","HL-C-1667-03","HL-C-1667-04","HL-C-1667-05","HL-C-1667-06","HL-C-1667-07"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-1667-01","HL-R-1667-02","HL-R-1667-03"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["命宫","兄弟宫","财帛宫","疾厄宫","官禄宫","田宅宫"],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["禄"],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","FINANCE_CASHFLOW","HEALTH_RISK","PROPERTY_HOME","PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":["HL_SELF_OTHER_PALACE","HL_HEALTH"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-1668","source_sequence":1668,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":7539,"source_line_end":7543,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四十八·紫微斗数·终极理则与大限流年应验全篇","parent_section":"五、我方与他方之损益论","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(二) 损益流向\n   我宫化入他方：为给人。他宫化入我方：为人给我。\n   我宫化禄入他宫，化忌在我方：表借贷投资必有损，不借贷则无妨。\n   我宫禄入我宫，忌入他宫：表损财，不可借贷投资。\n   禄忌全入我三方：较为不凶。冲三方：则凶。","raw_text_sha256":"891737b9f93ac08df19c1c53d28a8a6f85ce4a0993624ebdfc46f3a647d039f5","clause_ids":["HL-C-1668-01","HL-C-1668-02","HL-C-1668-03","HL-C-1668-04","HL-C-1668-05","HL-C-1668-06","HL-C-1668-07"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-1668-01","HL-R-1668-02","HL-R-1668-03","HL-R-1668-04","HL-R-1668-05","HL-R-1668-06"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","COMPARISON","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化禄","化忌","禄","忌"],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":[],"technique_ids":["HL_SELF_OTHER_PALACE"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":false,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-1669","source_sequence":1669,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":7545,"source_line_end":7552,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四十八·紫微斗数·终极理则与大限流年应验全篇","parent_section":"五、我方与他方之损益论","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(三) 他宫与我方之吉凶交织\n   他宫化禄或化忌入我三合方：表他人给我。\n   他宫一禄一忌入我命迁线：为“禄随忌走”，主损财，凶。\n   他宫忌入我方，而禄照我方：视为佳构，表朋友的钱归我所用。\n   禄忌同入我方：为凶。\n   禄忌同宫冲照我方：更凶。\n   禄入他方，忌入我方：损失较小。\n   禄入他方，忌冲我方：损失较大。","raw_text_sha256":"ae789720598897270d52e188adf86fb0e24058fb778c36d6abadf7f380885ec3","clause_ids":["HL-C-1669-01","HL-C-1669-02","HL-C-1669-03","HL-C-1669-04","HL-C-1669-05","HL-C-1669-06","HL-C-1669-07","HL-C-1669-08"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-1669-01","HL-R-1669-02","HL-R-1669-03","HL-R-1669-04","HL-R-1669-05","HL-R-1669-06"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["ALTERNATIVE","COMPARISON","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化禄","化忌","禄","忌"],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["PARTNERSHIP_NETWORK"],"technique_ids":["HL_SELF_OTHER_PALACE","HL_LU_JI_CAUSAL"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
