{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-1674","source_sequence":1674,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":7567,"source_line_end":7572,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四十八·紫微斗数·终极理则与大限流年应验全篇","parent_section":"七、迁移、灾厄与车祸","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"  迁移化忌入子田线：表意外之灾。入兄友线：被撞的是他人，是我撞人家。\n  命化忌入子田线、父疾线：健康有问题。\n  流年迁移化忌入本命父疾线：为出外损财，非被撞。\n  流迁化忌看车祸：得先看原盘有无发生意外之迹象，再看大限所落宫位来\n  决定，判断到底是损财还是伤身。\n  流年行入命迁线、子田线、父疾线：比较有事端。入父疾可能较有官非。","raw_text_sha256":"d7c9779a3d1c223290651a37a8320278d4277aa2d194077ff5daf2101e797e22","clause_ids":["HL-C-1674-01","HL-C-1674-02","HL-C-1674-03","HL-C-1674-04","HL-C-1674-05","HL-C-1674-06","HL-C-1674-07","HL-C-1674-08"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-1674-01","HL-R-1674-02","HL-R-1674-03","HL-R-1674-04","HL-R-1674-05","HL-R-1674-06"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","COMPARISON","SEQUENCE"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化忌","忌"],"temporal_tags":["本命","原盘","大限","流年"],"topic_tags":["HEALTH_RISK","MIGRATION_OUTSIDE"],"technique_ids":["HL_PARENT_DISEASE_DOCUMENT_LINE","HL_SIBLING_FRIEND_ACHIEVEMENT_LINE","HL_CHILD_PROPERTY_LINE","HL_HEALTH"],"result_term_candidates":["车祸"],"risk_tags":["ENDPOINT_CANDIDATE_ONLY"],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":true,"s02_translation_required":false}
