{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-1679","source_sequence":1679,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":7587,"source_line_end":7597,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四十八·紫微斗数·终极理则与大限流年应验全篇","parent_section":"九、桃花正论与疾厄忌星","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"   禄是想法，忌是实践。故同一宫化出之禄忌，皆需合参。\n   交友宫化忌入命、夫妻、子女、疾厄、田宅：叫“飞来桃花”。\n     入疾厄、田宅之桃花：较麻烦，具有粘性，会上车。\n     入夫妻、子女之桃花：不会上车。\n     若禄入疾厄，忌入子女：则会上车。\n   大限交友禄入子女或疾厄，而化忌入命或夫妻：主桃花十年。\n   例：交友禄入夫妻，忌入命：桃花亦然十年整。若子女宫有化科，还可能\n   跟她生了一个儿子。\n   交友化忌入夫妻：为桃花入宅。若为未婚人，表新娘提早到家同居；已婚\n   人为客兄带入厝。\n   科是风情，主桃花，入阴宫更验。科需要人家介绍，忌是无媒自召。","raw_text_sha256":"22598b0da0711e5bc01e1c58db2534fad130348fb7d85abe56e091ccb6e2b32f","clause_ids":["HL-C-1679-01","HL-C-1679-02","HL-C-1679-03","HL-C-1679-04","HL-C-1679-05","HL-C-1679-06","HL-C-1679-07","HL-C-1679-08","HL-C-1679-09","HL-C-1679-10","HL-C-1679-11","HL-C-1679-12","HL-C-1679-13","HL-C-1679-14","HL-C-1679-15","HL-C-1679-16"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-1679-01","HL-R-1679-02","HL-R-1679-03","HL-R-1679-04","HL-R-1679-05","HL-R-1679-06","HL-R-1679-07","HL-R-1679-08","HL-R-1679-09","HL-R-1679-10","HL-R-1679-11","HL-R-1679-12"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","CAUSAL","NEGATION","ALTERNATIVE","COMPARISON","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":["子女宫","交友宫"],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["化科","化忌","禄","科","忌"],"temporal_tags":["大限"],"topic_tags":["MARRIAGE_RELATION","CHILDREN_FERTILITY","HEALTH_RISK","PROPERTY_HOME","PARTNERSHIP_NETWORK"],"technique_ids":["HL_PEACH_BLOSSOM","HL_HEALTH"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
