{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-1683","source_sequence":1683,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":7608,"source_line_end":7612,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四十八·紫微斗数·终极理则与大限流年应验全篇","parent_section":"十、各类杂断集成","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(三) 星性与健康\n   紫微入父疾线最好，可解厄。\n   天相在命、福德最好。加紫微在福德，比较没有抱负。\n   天府在命主孤，落入疾厄较劳。\n   天梁在命、疾厄、福德：主长寿。","raw_text_sha256":"d5164c474acdab64cc66e7ce0ef17f8871458e1bdb4cd6d283b7f2702fa84d97","clause_ids":["HL-C-1683-01","HL-C-1683-02","HL-C-1683-03","HL-C-1683-04","HL-C-1683-05","HL-C-1683-06"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-1683-01","HL-R-1683-02","HL-R-1683-03"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["COMPARISON","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":["紫微","天府","天相","天梁"],"transformation_tags":[],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["HEALTH_RISK"],"technique_ids":["HL_PARENT_DISEASE_DOCUMENT_LINE","HL_HEALTH"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-1684","source_sequence":1684,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":7614,"source_line_end":7619,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四十八·紫微斗数·终极理则与大限流年应验全篇","parent_section":"十、各类杂断集成","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(四) 五行星曜类象\n   禄为金：主财、主寿、主才艺。\n   权为火：主才华、能干、霸道。\n   科为木：主科名巧艺。\n   忌为水：为服务业、买卖业，不可从事生产工厂。\n   科入水位（亥子）：为水生木，主得位。","raw_text_sha256":"11d3fcd2013e8ccf0f6e5203b5d5175c26dec2d35802735ba31e2ec1462bd43f","clause_ids":["HL-C-1684-01","HL-C-1684-02","HL-C-1684-03","HL-C-1684-04","HL-C-1684-05","HL-C-1684-06"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-1684-01","HL-R-1684-02"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["NEGATION","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":[],"transformation_tags":["禄","权","科","忌"],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["CHILDREN_FERTILITY"],"technique_ids":[],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
{"source_root_atom_id":"HL-A-1685","source_sequence":1685,"primary_authority_library":"S10","source_line_start":7621,"source_line_end":7627,"blank_lines_after":1,"parent_volume":"卷四十八·紫微斗数·终极理则与大限流年应验全篇","parent_section":"十、各类杂断集成","parent_subsection":"","raw_text":"(五) 嗜好与性格\n   嗜好看福德：坐贪狼好喝酒、打牌。\n   命、迁移、父母坐生年忌，再逢自化忌：为人较固执。\n   天刑坐命人：比较喜欢借贷。天刑会太阳，向男人借钱；会太阴，向女人\n   借。\n   生年忌在官禄，又逢自化权：主为人做事不择手段。财帛有此现象，为敢\n   赚也敢花。","raw_text_sha256":"616b8aaf568027b2ff128f6b3fdef020d903694b2714f1e77cf7f91cb052e0dc","clause_ids":["HL-C-1685-01","HL-C-1685-02","HL-C-1685-03","HL-C-1685-04","HL-C-1685-05","HL-C-1685-06","HL-C-1685-07","HL-C-1685-08","HL-C-1685-09","HL-C-1685-10"],"relation_ids":["HL-R-1685-01","HL-R-1685-02","HL-R-1685-03","HL-R-1685-04","HL-R-1685-05","HL-R-1685-06","HL-R-1685-07"],"relation_closure_status":"PASS","logical_operators":["CONDITION","NEGATION","COMPARISON","SEQUENCE","QUANTITY"],"palace_tags":[],"star_tags":["太阳","太阴","贪狼","天刑"],"transformation_tags":["化权","化忌","自化权","自化忌","禄","权","忌"],"temporal_tags":[],"topic_tags":["CAREER_WORK","FINANCE_CASHFLOW","MIGRATION_OUTSIDE","PARENT_FAMILY"],"technique_ids":["HL_SELF_TRANSFORM","HL_LOAN"],"result_term_candidates":[],"risk_tags":[],"contribution_mode":"CONDITIONAL_SOURCE_CANDIDATE","s17_required":true,"s18_review_required":false,"s02_translation_required":false}
